hadiths[352]{hadithnumber,text}:
3605,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah ney Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ki aulad mein sey Ismail (Alaihissalam) ka intikhaab farmaya padhi. aur Ismail (Alaihissalam) ki aulad mein sey bani Kinaana ka, aur bani Kinaana mein sey Quraish ka, aur Quraish mein sey bani Haashim ka, aur bani Haashim mein sey mera intikhaab farmaya.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3606,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah taala ney Ismail (Alaihissalam) ki aulad sey Kinaana ka intikhaab farmaya aur Kinaana sey Quraish ka aur Quraish mein sey Haashim ka aur bani Haashim mein sey mera intikhaab farmaya.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai.
3607,"mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! Quraish key log bethey aur unhoney Quraish mein apney hasab ka zikr kiya to aap ki misal khajoor key eik aisey darkht sey di jo kisi koodey-khaane par (uga) ho to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah taala ney makhluq ko paida kiya, usney is mein sey do girohon ko pasand kiya, aur mujhey un mein sab sey achchhey giroh (yani aulade Ismail) mein paida kiya, phir usney qabeelon ko chuna aur mujhey behtar qabiley mein sey kiya, phir gharon ko chuna aur mujhey un gharon mein sab sey behtar ghar mein kiya, to main zaati taur par bhi un mein sab sey behtar hun aur gharaney key aetbar sey bhi behtar hun.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai."
3608,"Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaye , goya unhoney koi chiz suni thi, to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam member par khadey huye aur farmaya : ''main kon hun?'' logon ney kaha : aap Allah key Rasool hain salamti ho aap par, aap ney farmaya : ''main Muhammad bin Abdullah bin Abdul-Muttalib hun, Allah ney makhluq ko paida kiya to mujhey unkey sab sey behtar makhluq mein kiya, phir unkey do giroh kiye to mujhey unkey behtar giroh mein kiya, phir unhen qabeelon mein baantaa to mujhey unkey sab sey behtar qabila mein kiya, phir unkey kaee ghar kiye to mujhey unkey sab sey behtar ghar mein kiya aur shakhsi taur par bhi mujhey un mein sab sey behtar banaya.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- jis tarah Ismail bin abi Khalid ney Yazeed bin abi Ziyad sey aur Yazeed bin abi Ziyad ney Abdullah bin Haris key wastey sey Abbas bin Abdul-Muttalib sey riwayat ki hai isi tarah Sufiyan Sory ney bhi Yazeed bin Abi Ziyad sey riwayat ki hai (wo yehi riwayat hai)."
3609,"logon ney puchha : Allah key Rasool ! nabuwat aap key liye kab wajib hui? to aap ney farmaya : ''jab Adam rooh aur jism key darmiyan they.''  (yani un ki paidaish ki tayyari ho rahi thi). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 2- is bab mein Maisraa Fajr sey bhi riwayat aai hai."
3610,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab log (qabron sey) uthaey jaeyngey to main pehla wo shakhs hunga jis sey zamin shaqq (phategi) hogi aur jab wo darbare Ilaahi mein ayengey to main unka khateeb hunga, aur jab wo mayus aur na-umeed ho jaeyngey to main unhen khushkhabri sunaney wala hunga, hamd ka parcham us din merey haath mein hoga, aur main apney Rab key nazdik aulade Adam mein sab sey behtar hun aur ye koi fakhr ki baat nahin.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
3611,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main pehla wo shakhs hunga jis sey zamin shaqq (phategi) hogi phir mujhey jannat key jodon mein sey eik joda pehnaya jaeyga, phir main arsh key daahini janib khada hunga, merey ilawa wahan makhluq mein sey koi aur khada nahin ho sakeyga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai."
3612,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah sey merey liye wasila ka sawal karo, logon ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! wasila kya hai? aap ney farmaya : '' ye jannat ka sab sey ooncha darja hai jisey sirf eik hi shakhs paa sakta hai aur mujhey ummid hai ke wo main hunga.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, iski sanad ziyada qawi nahin hai. 2- Kaab ghair maroof shakhs hain, hum Les bin Sulaim key ilawa kisi aur ko nahin jantey hain jisney un sey riwayat ki ho."
3613,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''anbiya mein meri misal eik aisey aadmi ki hai jisney eik ghar banaya aur usey bahut achchha banaya, mukammal aur nihayat khoobsurat banaya, lekin us main eik eent ki jagah chhod di, log is mein phirtey they aur uski khoobsurti ko dekh kar tajjub kartey they aur kehtey they, kaash! is eent ki jagah bhi puri ho jati, to main nabiyon mein aisey hi hun jaisi khaali jagah ki ye eent hai.''"
3614,"unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : ''jab tum muazzan ki aawaz suno to wohi kaho jo muazzan kehta hai padhi. phir merey ooper salaat ( durood ( bhejo kyonkey jisney merey ooper eik baar durood bheja to Allah is par das baar apni rahmatein nazil farmaeyga , phir merey liye wasila maango kyonkey wo jannat main eik ( aisa buland ( darja hai jis key laaiq Allah key bandon mein sey sirf eik banda hai aur main ummid karta hun ke wo banda main hi hun aur jisney merey liye (Allah sey) wasila manga to uskey liye meri shafaat halal ho gaee.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain : is sanad mein mazkur Abdur-Rehman bin Juber Qarshi, Misri aur Madni hain aur nafeer key potey Abdur-Rehman bin Juber Shaami hain."
3615,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main qiyamat key din aulade Adam ka sardar hunga aur merey haath mein hamd ka parcham hoga aur is par mujhey ghamand nahin, aur Adam aur Adam key ilawa jitney bhi Nabi hongey sab merey parcham key nichey hongey, aur main pehla wo shakhs hunga jis key liye zamin shaqq hogi (phategi), aur sab sey pehley qabr sey mein uthoon ga aur is par mujhey ghamand nahin.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees main eik waqia mazkur hai. 2- isey isi sanad sey abu-Nazara sey riwayat hai, wo isey ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kartey hain."
3616,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key as-haab mein sey kuchh log bethey aap key hujrey sey nikalney ka intizar kar rahey they, kehtey hain : phir aap nikley yahan tak ke jab aap unkey qarib aaye to unhen aapas mein behes kartey suna , aap ney un ki baaten sunin , koi keh raha tha, tajjub hai Allah ney apni makhluq mein sey Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ko apna dost banaya , doosrey ney kaha : Musa sey uska kalam karna kitna ziyada tajjub khez maamla hai, aur eik ney kaha : Esa (Alaihissalam) Allah ka kalima aur uski rooh hain, aur eik doosrey ney kaha : Adam ko Allah ney to chun liya hai, to aap nikal kar unkey samney aaye aur unhen salam kiya aur farmaya : ''main ney tumhari baaten sun li hain aur Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) key khaleelullah honey par tajjub mein padney ko bhi, waqaee wo aisey hi hain aur Musa (Alaihissalam) key Allah key naji Allah honey par , aur wo bhi waqae aisey hi hain aur Esa (Alaihissalam) key  Allah ke kalima aur rooh Allah honey par , aur wo bhi waqae aisey hi hain aur Adam key Allah ka barguzeeda honey par , aur wo bhi waqae aisey hi hain, sun lo ! main Allah ka Habib hun aur is par mujhey ghamand nahin, qiyamat key din hamd ka parcham merey haath mein hoga aur is par mujhey ghamand nahin aur qiyamat key din main pehla wo shakhs hunga jo shafaat (sifarish) kerega aur jiski shafaat (sifarish) sab sey pehley qubul ki jaeygi aur is par mujhey ghamand nahin aur main pehla wo shakhs hunga jo jannat ki kundi hilaaeyga to Allah merey liye jannat ko khol dega, phir wo mujhey is mein dakhil kerega aur merey sath fuqaraa momineen hongey aur is par mujhey ghamand nahin aur main aglon aur pichhlon mein sab sey ziyada moazziz hun aur is par mujhey ghamand nahin.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai."
3617,"Torat mein Muhammad Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key ahwaal likhey huye hain aur ye bhi ke Esa bin Maryam unhin key sath dafn kiye jaeyngey. abu-Quteba kehtey hain ke Abu Maudud ney kaha : hujra Mubarak main eik qabr ki jagah baqi hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, sanad mein Raavi ney Usman bin Zuhaak kaha aur mashhoor Zuhaak bin Usman Madni hai."
3618,"jab wo din huwa jis mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ( pehley pehal ( Madina mein dakhil huye to uski har chiz pur-noor ho gaee , phir jab wo din aaya jis mein aap ki wafat hui to uski har chiz taareek (andheri) ho gaee aur abhi hamney aap key dafn sey haath bhi nahin jhaadey they ke hamarey dil badal gaey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib sahih hai."
3619,"main aur Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam dono waqiaa-feel key saal paida huye, wo kehtey hain : Usman bin Affaan ney Qabas bin Ashim (jo qabila bani Yaamar bin Les key eik fard hain) sey puchha ke aap badey hain ya Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam? to unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam mujh sey badey hain aur paidaish mein, main aap sey pehley hun padhi. , Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam haathi waley saal mein paida huye, meri maa mujhey us jagah par ley gaeen (jahan Ibrahaa key haathiyon par parindon ney kankariyaan barsai thin) to mainey dekha ke haathiyon ki leed badli hui hai aur sabz (hara) rang ki ho gaee hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf Muhammad bin Is-haq ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
3620,"Abu-Talib Sham ki taraf ( tijarat ki gharz sey) nikley , Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam bhi Quraish key boodhon mein unkey sath nikley , jab ye log Buhira raahib key paas pahunchey to wahin padaw dal diya aur apni sawaariyon key kajawey khol diye, to raahib apney girjaghar sey nikal kar unkey paas aaya halanke is sey pehley ye log uskey paas sey guzartey they, lekin wo kabhi un ki taraf mutawajjeh nahin hota tha, aur na unkey paas aata tha, kehtey hain : to ye log apni sawariyan abhi khol hi rahey they ke raahib ney unkey bech sey ghustey huye aa kar Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka haath pakad liya aur bola : ye sarey jahan key sardar hain, ye sarey jahan key sardar hain, ye sarey jahan key rab key Rasool hain, Allah unhen sarey jahan key liye rehmat bana kar bhejeyga , to us sey Quraish key boodhon ney puchha : tumhen ye kaisey malum huwa? to usney kaha : jab tum log us tiley sey utrey to koi darkht aur pathar aisa nahin raha jo sajdey mein na gir pada ho, aur ye dono sirf Nabi hi ko sajda kya kartey hain, aur main inhen mohare-nabuwat sey pahchaanta hun jo shaaney ki haddi key sirey key nichey seb key maanind hai, phir wo wapis gaya aur unkey liye khana tayyar kya, jab wo khana ley kar unkey paas aaya to aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam oont charaney gaey they to usney kaha : kisi ko bhej do ke in ko bula kar laye, chunanche aap aaye aur eik badli aap par saya kiye huye thi, jab aap logon key qarib huye to unhen darkht key sayey mein pehley hi sey bethey paya , phir jab aap beth gaey to darkht ka saya aap par jhuk gaya is par raahib bol utha : dekho ! darkht ka saya aap par jhuk gaya hai, phir raahib unkey samney khada raha aur un sey qism dey kar keh raha tha ke unhen Rome na ley jaao isliye ke Rome key log dekhtey hi unhen unkey osaaf sey pehchan leingey aur unhen qatl kar dalengey, phir wo muda to dekha ke saat aadmi hain jo Rome sey aaye huye hain to usney badh kar un sab ka istaqbal kya aur puchha aap log kyon aaye hain? un logon ney kaha : hum us Nabi key liye aaye hain jo is mahina mein aaney wala hai, aur koi raasta aisa baqi nahin bacha hai jiski taraf kuch na kuch log na bhejey gaey hon, aur jab hamen tumharey is raastey par iski khabar lagi to hum tumhari us raah par bhejey gaey, to usney puchha : kya tumharey peechey koi aur hai jo tum sey behtar ho? un logon ney kaha : hamen to tumharey is raasta par uski khabar lagi to hum is par ho liye usney kaha : achcha ye bataao ke Allah jis Amr ka faisla farma ley kya logon mein sey usey koi taal sakta hai? un logon ney kaha : nahin, usney kaha : phir tum us sey baiat karo, aur uskey sath raho , phir wo Arbon ki taraf mutawajjeh ho kar bola : main tum sey Allah ka wasta dey kar poochhta hun ke tum mein sey uska wali kon hai? logon ney kaha : Abu-Talib , to wo unhen barabar qism dilata raha yahan tak ke Abu-Talib ney unhen wapis Makka lota diya aur abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney aap key sath Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko bhi bhej diya aur raahib ney aap ko Keek aur zaitun ka tosha diya . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
3621,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam par wahi nazil ki gaee to aap chaalis saal key they, phir aap Makka mein 13 saal tak rahey aur Madina mein das saal tak , aur aap ki wafat hui to aap 63 saal key they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3622,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki wafat hui to aap painsath (65) saal key they padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : isi tarah sey hum sey Muhammad bin Bishr ney bayan kya hai aur un sey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ney usi key misl riwayat ki hai.
3623,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam na bahut lambey qad waley they na bahut naatey aur na nihayat safed, na bilkul gehun goon , aap key sar key baal na ghunghraaley they na bilkul sidhey , Allah Taala ney aap ko chalisweyn saal key shuru mein maboos farmaya , phir Makka mein aap das baras rahey aur Madina mein das baras aur sathwein baras padhi. key shuru mein Allah ney aap ko wafat di aur aap key sar aur dadhi mein bees baal bhi safed nahin rahey hongey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3624,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Makka main eik pathar hai jo mujhey un raaton mein jin mein Nabi banakar bheja gaya tha salam kya karta tha, usey main ab bhi pahchaanta hun '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
3625,"hum Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath eik badey bartan mein subh sey Sham tak khatey rahey , das aadmi uthtey they aur das bethtey they, hamney ( Samra sey) kaha : to us piyala numa badey bartan mein kuch badhaya nahin jata tha? unhoney kaha : tumhen tajjub kis baat par hai? is mein badhaya nahin jata tha magar wahan sey , aur unhoney apney haath sey aasman ki janib ishara kya padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3626,"mein Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath Makka mein tha, jab hum uskey baaz atraaf mein nikley to jo bhi pahad aur darkht aap key samney aatey sabhi ''Assalamualaik ya Rasoolullah '' kehtey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- kaee logon ney ye hadees Waleed bin abi soor sey riwayat ki hai aur un sab ney «an Ibaad abi Yazid» kaha hai, aur unhi mein sey farwa bin abi al-Mughra bhi hain padhi. ."
3627,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam khajoor key eik taney sey tek laga kar khutba detey they, phir logon ney aap key liye eik member tayyar kar diya, aap ney is par khutba diya to wo tana roney laga jaisey oontni roti hai jab Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney utar kar is par haath phera tab wo chup huwa padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Anas wali hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein abi , Jabir , ibne-Umar , Sehal bin Saad , ibne-Abbas aur Umme-Salma (Raziallahu Anha) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
3628,"eik dehati Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaya aur usney kaha : kaisey main jaanun ke aap Nabi hain? aap ney farmaya : '' agar main us khajoor key darkht ki us tehni ko bula lun to kya tum merey barey mein Allah key Rasool honey ki gawahi dogey ? '' chunanche Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney usey bulaya to wo ( tehni ( khajoor key darkht sey utar kar Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key samney gir padi , phir aap ney farmaya : '' lot ja to wo wapis chali gaee ye dekh kar wo dehati Islam ley aaya ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai."
3629,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney apna daste-Mubarak merey chehrey par phera aur merey liye dua farmaey, azra kehtey hain : wo eik so bees saal tak pahunchey hain phir bhi unkey sar key sirf chand baal safed huye they padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- abu-Zaid ka naam Amr bin akhtab hai."
3630,"abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ney Umme Sulem Raziallahu anhuma sey kaha : mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki aawaz suni , wo kamzor thi, mujhey mehsus hota hai ke aap bhookey hain, kya tumharey paas koi chiz khaney ki hai? unhoney kaha : ji haan , to unhoney jo ki kuch rotiyaan nikalen phir apni odhni nikali aur uskey kuch hissey mein rotiyon ko lapet kar merey haath yani baghal key nichey chupa din aur odhni ka kuch hissey mujhey udha diya, phir mujhey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas bheja , jab main usey ley kar aap key paas aaya to mujhey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam masjid mein bethey miley aur aap key sath kuch aur log bhi they, to main ja kar unkey paas khada ho gaya, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney puchha : '' kya tumhen abu-Talha ney bheja hai? ''mainey arz kya : ji haan , aap ney puchha : '' khana ley kar ? ''main ney kaha : ji haan , to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un tamam logon sey jo aap key sath they farmaya : '' utho chalo '' , chunanche wo sab chal padey aur main unkey aagey aagey chala, yahan tak ke main abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aaya aur unhen uski khabar di, abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Umme Sulem ! Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam tashrif ley aaye hain, aur log bhi aap key sath hain aur hamarey paas kuch nahin jo hum unhen khilaeyn, Umme Sulem ney kaha : Allah aur uskey Rasool ko khub malum hai, to abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) chaley aur aa kar Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey miley, to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam aaye aur abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) aap key sath they, yahan tak ke dono andar aa gaey, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Umme Sulem ! jo tumharey paas hai usey ley aao'' , chunanche wo wohi rotiyaan leykar aain, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney unhen todney ka hukm diya, chunanche wo todi gaeen aur Umme Sulem ney apney ghi ki kuppi ko is par ondha kar diya aur usey is mein chipad diya, phir is par Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney padha jo Allah ney padhwana chaha, phir aap ney farmaya : '' das aadmiyon ko andar aaney do'', to unhoney unhen aaney diya aur wo kha kar aasooda ho gaey, phir wo nikal gaey, phir aap ney farmaya : '' das ko andar aaney do '' , to unhoney unhen aaney diya wo bhi kha kar khub aasooda ho gaey aur nikal gaey, is tarah sarey logon ney khub pet bharkar khaya aur wo sabkey sab sattar ya assi aadmi they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3631,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko dekha , Asr ka waqt ho gaya tha, logon ney wuzu ka pani dhoondha, lekin wo nahin paa sakey, itney mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas kuch wuzu ka pani laya gaya, to Rasulullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney us bartan mein apna haath rakha aur logon ko hukm diya ke wo us sey wuzu keren, wo kehtey hain : to mainey aap ki ungliyon key nichey sey pani ubaltey dekha , phir logon ney wuzu kya yahan tak ke un mein ka jo sab sey aakhiri shakhs tha usney bhi wuzu kar liya . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Anas ki ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Imran bin Husain, ibne-Masood , Jabir aur Ziyad bin Haris Sudaai (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
3632,"pehli wo chiz jis sey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki nabuwat ki ibtida hui aur jis waqt Allah ney apney ezaz sey aap ko nawazney aur aap key zariey bandon par apni rehmat o bakhshish ka irada kya wo ye thi ke aap jo bhi khuwab dekhtey they uski tabeer subh key po phatney ki tarah zahir ho jati thi, phir aap ka haal aisa hi raha jab tak Allah ney chaha, un dino khilwat o tanhai aap ko aisi marghoob thi ke itni marghoob koi aur chiz na thi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
3633,"tum log Allah ki nishaniyon ko azab samajhtey ho aur hum Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key zamaney mein usey barkat samajhtey they, hum Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath khana khatey they aur hum khaney ko tasbih padhtey suntey they, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas eik bartan laya gaya is mein aap ney apna haath rakha to aap ki ungliyon key beech sey pani ubalney laga, phir Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aao is barkat pani sey wuzu karo aur ye ba-barkat aasman sey nazil ho rahi hai, yahan tak ke hum sab ney wuzu kar liya ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3634,"Haris bin Hisham (Raziallahu anhu) ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey puchha : aap key paas wahi kaisey aati hai? Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''kabhi-kabhi wo merey paas ghanti ki aawaz padhi. ki tarah aati hai aur ye merey liye ziyada sakht hoti hai padhi. aur kabhi kabhi farishta merey samney aadmi ki shakal mein aata hai aur mujh sey kalam karta hai, to wo jo kehta hai usey main yad kar leta hun, Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) kehti hain : chunanche mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko sakht jadey key din mein aap par wahi utartey dekhi jab wo wahi khatam hoti to aap ki peshani par paseena aaya ho . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3635,"mainey kisi shakhs ko jis key baal kaan ki lo key nichey hon surkh jodey padhi. mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ziyada khoobsurat nahin dekha, aap key baal aap key dono kandhon sey lagey hotey they padhi. , aur aap key dono kandhon mein kafi fasla hota tha padhi. , na aap pasta qad they na bahut lambey 4- Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3636,"eik shakhs ney Bara sey puchha : kya Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka chehra Mubarak talwaar ki tarah tha? unhoney kaha : nahin, balke chaand ki maanind tha . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3637,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam na lambey they na pasta qad, aapki hatheliyan aur paaon gosht sey pur they, aap badey sar aur motey jodon waley they, (yani ghutney aur kohniyaan gosht sey pur aur farba thin), seeney sey naaf tak bareek baal they, jab chaltey to aagey jhukey huye hotey mano aap ooper sey nichey utar rahey hain, mainey na aap sey pehley aur na aap key baad kisi ko aap jaisa dekha . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3638,"Ali (Raziallahu anhu) jab Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka huliya bayan kartey to kehtey : na aap bahut lambey they na bahut pasta qad , balke logon mein darmiyani qad key they, aap key baal na bahut ghungriyaale they na bilkul sidhey , balke un dono key beech mein they, na aap bahut motey they aur na chehra bilkul gol tha, haan is mein kuchh golaae zarur thi, aap gorey safed surkhi maael, siyah chashm (aankh), lambi palkon waley , badey jodon waley aur badey shaane waley they, aap key jism par ziyada baal nahin they, sirf baalon ka eik khat seene sey naaf tak khinchaa huwa tha, dono hatheliyan aur dono qadam gosht sey pur they jab chaltey zamin par pair jama kar chaltey, palat'tey to purey badan key sath palat'tey , aap key dono shaanon key bich mein mohare nabuwat thi, aap khaatimul-nabiyeen they, logon mein aap sab sey ziyada sakhi they, aap khuley dil key they, yani aap ka Sina bughz aur hasad sey aayene key maanind paak aur saaf hota tha, aur sab sey ziyada sach bolney waley, naram mizaj aur sab sey behtar rehan sehan waley they, jo aap ko yakayak dekhta dar jata aur jo aap ko jaan aur samajh kar aap sey ghul mil jata wo aap sey mohabbat karney lagta , aap ki khubiyon ko bayaan karney wala kehta : na aap sey pehley mainey kisi ko aap jaisa dekha hai aur na aap key baad. Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, iski sanad muttasil nahin hai. 2- (Nusaai key Shaikh) abu Jaafar kehtey hain : mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key huliya Mubarak ki tafseer mein Asmaee ko kehtey huye suna ke « الممغط » key maana lambaai mein janey waley key hain, mainey eik Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) ko suna wo keh raha tha (تمغط فی نشابة) yani usney apna teer bahut ziyada khincha aur « متردد » aisa shakhs hai jis ka badan thigney-pan ki wajeh sey baaz baaz (aapas) mein ghusa huwa ho aur « قطط » sakht ghungryaale baal ko kehtey hain, aur « رَجِل » us aadmi ko kehtey hain jis key baalon mein thodi khameedgi ho aur « مطہم » aisey jism waley ko kehtey hain jo mota aur ziyada gosht wala ho aur « مکلثم » jis ka chehra gol ho aur « مشدب » wo shakhs hai jiski peshani mein surkhi ho aur « ادعج » wo shakhs hai jis key aakhon ki siyahi khub kaali ho aur « اہدب » wo hai jiski palken lambi hon aur « کتد » dono shaanon key milney ki jagah ko kehtey hain aur « مسربة » wo bareek baal hain jo eik khat ki tarah Sina sey naaf tak chaley gaey hon aur « شثن » wo shakhs hai jis key hatheliyon aur pairon ki ungliyan moti hon , aur « تقلع » sey murad pair jama jama kar taqat sey chalna hai aur « صبب » utarney key maana mein hai, Arab kehtey hain « انحدر نافی صبوب وصبب » yani hum bulandi sey utrey (جلیل المشاش) sey murad shaanon key sirey hain, yani aap buland shaane waley they, aur « ishrat » sey murad rehan-sehan hai aur « عشیرہ » key maana rehan-sehan waley key hain aur « بدیھة » key maana yakayak aur yakbaargi key hain, Arab kehtey hain « بَدَهْتُهُ بِأَمْرٍ » main eik maamle ko ley kar uskey paas achcha aaya."
3639,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam tumhari tarah jaldi jaldi nahin boltey they balke aap aisi guftgu kartey jis mein thehrao hota tha, jo aap key paas betha hota wo usey yad kar leta . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, hum isey sirf Zohri ki riwayat sey jantey hain, 2- usey Yunus bin Yazeed ney bhi Zohri sey riwayat kya hai."
3640,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ( kabhi-kabhi (eik kalma teen baar dohraatey they taake usey ( achi tarah ( samajh liya jaey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, hum isey sirf Abdullah bin Musanna ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
3641,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey badh kar muskuraney wala mainey kisi ko nahin dekha . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai.
3642,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki hansi sirf muskurahat hoti thi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees sahih gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey Les bin Saad ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
3643,"meri khaala mujhey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas ley kar gaeen , unhoney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! mera bhanja bimar hai, to aap ney merey sar par haath pheraa aur merey liye barkat ki dua farmaee, aap ney wuzu kiya to mainey aap key wuzu ka bacha huwa pani pi liya , phir main aap key peechhey khada ho gaya, aur mainey aap key dono shaanon key darmiyan mohre-nubuwat dekhi wo chhappar khat (key pardey) ki ghundi ki tarah thi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : kabootar key andey ko « zar » kaha jata hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Salman Qurra bin Ayas Muzni , Jabir bin Samura, Abu Ramsaa , Barida Aslami , Abdullah bin Sarjis , Amr bin Akhtab aur abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallauh anhum) sey ahadees aai hain."
3644,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki mohre-nubuwat yani jo aap key dono shaanon key darmiyan thi kabootar key andey key maanind surkh rang ki eik gilti thi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
3645,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki dono pindliyan munasib baareeki liye huye thin aur aap ka hasnaa sirf muskurana tha, aur jab main aap ko dekhta to kehta ke aap aakhon mein surma lagaey huye hain, halanke aap surma nahin lagaey hotey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai."
3646,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka munh Mubarak kushada tha, aap ki aankh key dorey surkh they aur eidiyaan kam gosht wali thin. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3647,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam kushada munh waley they, aap ki aankh key dorey surkh aur eidiyaan kam gosht wali thin. Shoba kehtey hain : mainey Simaak sey puchha : « ضليع الفم » key kya maana hain? to unhoney kaha : uskey maana kushada munh key hain, mainey puchha « أشكل العينين » key kya maana hain? to unhoney kaha : uskey maana badi aankh waley key hain, wo kehtey hain : mainey puchha : « منهوش العقب » key kya maana hain? to unhoney kaha : kam gosht key hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3648,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ziyada khoobsurat kisi ko nahin dekha , goya aap key chehre par suraj phir raha hai, aur na mainey kisi ko aap sey ziyada tez raftaar dekha , goya zamin aap key liye lapet di jati thi, hamein aap key sath chalney mein zahmat uthaani padti thi aur aap koi diqqat mehsus kiye baghair chaley jatey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai."
3649,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''anbiya merey samney pesh kiye gaey to Musa (Alaihissalam) eik chharere jawan they, goya wo qabila Shanu key eik fard hain aur mainey Esa bin Maryam (Alaihissalam) ko dekha to mainey jin logon ko dekha hai un mein sab sey ziyada un sey mushaabihat rakhney waley Urwa bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) hain aur mainey Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ko dekha to un sey ziyada mushaabihat rakhney wala tumhara ye sathi hai padhi. , aur us sey murad aap khud apni zaat ko letey they, aur mainey Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ko dekha to jin logon ko mainey dekha hai un mein sab sey ziyada un sey mushaabihat rakhney waley Dahiya Kalbi hain, ye Khalifa Kalbi key betey hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
3650,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki wafat hui to aap painsath (65) saal key they.
3651,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki wafat hui to aap painsath (65) saal key they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai.
3652,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Makka mein tera (13) saal rahey yani aap par tera saal tak ""wahi"" ki jati rahi aur aap ki wafat (63) saal ki umr mein hui. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki ye hadees Amr bin Dinar ki riwayat sey Hasan gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Aaisha , Anas aur Daghfal bin Hanzala (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain. - aur Daghfal ka Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey na to samaa (sun'na), sahih hai aur na hi dekha hai."
3653,mainey Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ko khutba detey huye suna wo keh rahey they : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki wafat hui to aap taresath (63) saal key they aur abu-Bakar aur umr Raziallahu anhuma bhi (63) saal key they aur main bhi (is waqt) (63) saal ka hun. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
3654,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki wafat hui to aap taresath (63) saal key they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- aur isey Zohri key bhatijey (Muhammad bin Abdullah bin Muslim) ney bhi Zohri sey aur Zohri ney Urwa key wastey sey Aaisha sey isi key jaisi riwayat ki hai.
3655,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main har khaleel ki « خلت » (dosti) sey bari hun aur agar main kisi ko khaleel (dost) banata to ibne-Abi Qahaafa ko , yani Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko khaleel banata , aur tumhara ye sathi Allah ka khaleel hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein abu Saeed Khudri , Abu-Hurera , ibn Zuber aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
3656,Abu-Bakar hamarey sardar hain aur hum mein sab sey behtar hain aur wo hum mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko sab sey ziyada mehbub they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees sahih gharib hai.
3657,"mainey Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey puchha : Sahaba mein sey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko sab sey ziyada kon mehbub they? unhoney kaha : abu-Bakar , mainey puchha : phir kon ? unhoney kaha : umr , mainey puchha : phir kon ? kaha : phir abu-Ubaida bin Jarrah , mainey puchha : phir kon ? to wo khamosh rahin. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3658,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''buland darjaat walon ko (jannat mein) jo unkey nichey hongey , aisey hi dekhengey jaisey tum aasman key ufaq par tulu honey waley sitarey ko dekhtey ho aur abu-Bakar aur umr Raziallahu anhuma dono unhi mein sey hongey aur kya hi khub hain dono.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai, ye hadees dusri sanadon sey bhi Atiya key wastey sey abu Saeed Khudri sey aai hai."
3659,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik din khutba diya to farmaya : ''eik shakhs ko uskey Rab ney ikhtiyar diya ke wo duniya mein jitna rehna chahey rahey aur jitna khana chahey kha ley ya apney Rab sey milney ko (tarjeeh dey) to usney apney Rab sey milney ko pasand kiya, wo kehtey hain : ye sun kar abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ro padey, to Sahaba ney kaha : kya tumhen us boodhey key roney par tajjub nahin hota jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik nek bandey ka zikr kiya ke uskey Rab ney do baaton mein sey eik ka usey ikhtiyar diya ke wo duniya mein rahey ya apney Rab sey miley, to usney apney Rab sey mulaqat ko pasand kiya. abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) un mein sab sey ziyada un baaton ko jan'ney waley they jo Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya (Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki baat sun kar) Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : balke hum apney baap dada , apney maal sab ko aap par qurban kar dengey, to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''koi aadmi aisa nahin jo ibne-Abi Qahaafa sey badh kar mera haq sohbat ada karney wala ho aur merey ooper apna maal kharch karney wala ho, agar main kisi ko khaleel (gehra dost) banata to ibne-Abi Qahaafa ko dost banata, lekin (hamarey aur unkey darmiyan) eman ki dosti mojud hai.'' ye kalima aap ney do ya teen baar farmaya, phir farmaya : ''tumhara ye sathi (yani khud) Allah ka khaleel (dost) hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat aai hai aur ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- ye hadees abu Awaana key wastey sey Abdul-Malik bin Umer sey eik dusri sanad sey bhi aai hai, aur « أمن إلينا » mein (إلى) key maana mein hai, yani mujh par sab sey ziyada ehsan karney wala."
3660,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney member par beth kar farmaya : ''eik bandey ko Allah ney ikhtiyar diya ke wo duniya ki ranageeni ko pasand karey ya un chizon ko jo Allah key paas hain.''  to usney un chizon ko ikhtiyar kiya jo Allah key paas hain, usey suna to abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! hamney apney baap dada aur apni maaon ko aap par qurban kiya padhi. hamein tajjub huwa, logon ney kaha is boodhey ko dekho ! Allah key Rasool eik aisey bandey key barey mein khabar dey rahey hain jisey Allah ney ye ikhtiyar diya ke wo ya to duniya ki rangeeni ko apna ley ya Allah key paas jo kuchh hai usey apna ley, aur ye keh rahey hain ke hamney apney aabaa-o-ijdaad aur maaon ko aap par qurban kiya, jis bandey ko Allah ney ikhtiyar diya wo khud Allah key Rasool they, aur abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) usey hum mein sab sey ziyada jaan'ney waley they, abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki baat sun kar Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''sab sey badh kar mera haqe-sohbat ada karney waley aur sab sey ziyada merey ooper apna maal kharch karney waley abu-Bakar hain, agar main kisi ko khaleel (gehra dost) banata , to abu-Bakar ko banata lekin Islam ka bhai-chaara hi kafi hai aur masjid mein (yani masjid ki taraf) koi khidki baqi na rahey siwaye abu-Bakar ki khidki key. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3661,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''kisi ka hamarey ooper koi aisa ehsan nahin jisey mainey chuka na diya ho siwaye abu-Bakar key , kyonkey unka hamarey ooper itna bada ehsan hai ke jis ka pura pura badla qiyamat key din unhen Allah hi dega , kisi key maal sey kabhi bhi mujhey itna faeyda nahin pahuncha jitna mujhey abu-Bakar key maal ney pahunchaya hai, agar main kisi ko khaleel (gehra dost) bananey wala hota to abu-Bakar ko khaleel banata, sun lo tumhara ye sathi (yani khud) Allah ka khaleel hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai."
3662,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''iqtidaa karo un dono ki jo merey baad hongey, yani abu-Bakar o umr ki.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Masood sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- Sufiyan Sory ney ye hadees Abdul-Malik bin Umer sey aur Abdul-Malik bin Umer ney Rabee key azad karda ghulam key wastey sey Rabee sey aur Rabee ney Huzefa key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai."
3663,"hum log Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas bethey huye they to aap ney farmaya : ''main nahin janta ke main tumharey darmiyan kab tak rahunga, lihaza tum log un dono ki perwi karo jo merey baad hongey aur aap ney abu-Bakar o umr Raziallahu anhuma ki janib ishara kya ''."
3664,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney abu-Bakar o umr Raziallahu anhuma key silsiley mein farmaya : '' ye dono jannat key adhed Umr walon key sardar hongey, chahey wo agley hon ya pichley, siwaye anbiya o rasulon key, (aap ney farmaya :) '' Ali un dono ko is baat ki khabar mat dena ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai."
3665,"main Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath tha achcha abu-Bakar o umr Raziallahu anhuma namudaar huye, to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''ye dono jannat key adhed umr key logon key sardar hain, chahey wo agley hon ya pichley, siwaye anbiya o rasulon key lekin Ali ! tum unhen na batana''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai, 2- Waleed bin Muhammad hadees bayan karney mein zaeef hain aur Ali bin Husein ney Ali sey nahin suna hai, 3- Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey ye hadees is sanad key ilawa dusri sanad sey bhi aai hai, 4- is bab mein Anas aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
3666,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' abu-Bakar o umr jannat key adhed umr key logon key sardar hain, chahey wo agley hon ya pichley, siwaye nabiyon aur Rasulon key, lekin Ali ! tum unhen na batana ''."
3667,"abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : kya main wo shakhs nahin hun jo sabsey pehley Islam laya? kya main aisi aisi khoobiyon ka Malik nahin hun? Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- baaz ney ye hadees Shoba sey, Shoba ney Jariri sey, Jariri ney abu-Nazara sey riwayat ki hai, wo kehtey hain : abu-Bakar ney kaha , aur ye ziyada sahih hai."
3668,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam muhajrin o ansaar mein sey apney Sahaba key paas nikal kar aatey aur wo bethey hotey, un mein abu-Bakar o umr Raziallahu anhuma bhi hotey, to un mein sey koi apni nigah aap ki taraf nahin uthata tha, siwaye abu-Bakar o umr Raziallahu anhuma key ye dono aap ko dekhtey aur muskuraatey aur aap un dono ko dekhtey aur muskuraatey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- is hadees ko hum sirf Hakam bin Atiya ki riwayat sey jantey hain, 3- baaz muhaddeseen ney Hakam bin Atiya key barey mein kalam kya hai."
3669,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam eik din nikley aur masjid mein dakhil huye, abu-Bakar o umr Raziallahu anhuma mein sey eik aap key daain janib they aur doosrey baain janib , aur aap un dono ka haath pakdey huye they aap ney farmaya : ''isi tarah hum qiyamat key din uthaey jaeyngey''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- Saeed bin Muslima muhaddeseen key nazdik qawi nahin hain, 3- ye hadees is sanad key ilawa dusri sanad sey bhi Nafey key wastey sey ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey aai hai."
3670,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) sey farmaya : '' tum hoze-kausar par merey rafeeq hogey jaisa ke ghaar mein merey rafeeq they ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan, sahih, gharib hai."
3671,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney abu-Bakar o umr Raziallahu anhuma ko dekha to farmaya : '' ye dono ( Islam key ( kaan aur aankh hain ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees mursal hai Abdullah bin hantab ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko nahin paya , padhi. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
3672,"Nabi akram ney farmaya : '' abu-Bakar sey kaho ke wo logon ko namaz padhaein'' , is par Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! abu-Bakar jab aap ki jagah ( namaz padhaaney ( khadey hongey to roney ki wajeh sey logon ko qirat nahin suna sakengey padhi. , isliye aap umr ko hukm dijiye ki wo namaz padhaein , phir aap ney farmaya : '' abu-Bakar ko hukm do ke wo logon ko namaz padhaein ''. Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) kehti hain : to mainey Hafsa sey kaha : tum un sey kaho ke abu-Bakar jab aap ki jagah khadey hongey to logon ko roney key sabab qirat nahin suna sakengey , isliye aap umr ko hukm den ke wo logon ko namaz padhaein , to Hafsa ney ( aisa hi ( kya, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' tum wohi to ho jinhoney Yusuf (Alaihissalam) ko tang kya, abu-Bakar sey kaho ke wo logon ko namaz padhaein , to Hafsa ney Aaisha sey) bator shikayat ( kaha ke mujhey tum sey kabhi koi bhalai nahin pahunchi . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Masood , abu-Musa Ash-ari, ibne-Abbas , Salim bin Ubaid aur Abdullah bin Zamaa (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
3673,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' kisi qom key liye munasib nahin ke abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki mojudgi mein unkey siwa koi aur un ki imaamat karey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai.
3674,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo shakhs Allah ki raah mein joda kharch kerega usey jannat mein pukara jaeyga ke aey Allah key bandey ! ye wo khair hai) jisey terey liye tayyar kya gaya hai) to jo ehal salaat mein sey hoga usey salaat key darwazey sey pukara jaeyga, aur jo ehale-jihad mein sey hoga usey jihad key darwazey sey pukara jaeyga, aur jo ehal sadqa mein sey hoga usey sadqa key darwazey sey pukara jaeyga, aur jo ehal siyaam mein sey hoga, wo baabe-Rayyan sey pukara jaeyga, is par abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : merey maa baap aap par fida hon , uski koi zarurat nahin ke kisi ko un sarey darwazon sey pukara jaey ( isliye ke eik darwazey sey dakhil ho jana kafi hai) magar kya koi aisa bhi hoga jo un sabhi darwazon sey pukara jaeyga ? aap ney farmaya : '' haan , aur mujhey ummid hai ke tum unhi mein sey hogey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3675,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hamen sadqa karney ka hukm diya aur ittifaq sey un dino merey paas maal bhi tha, mainey ( dil mein) kaha : agar main abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) sey kisi din aagey badh sakunga to aaj key din aagey badh jaaunga, phir main apna aadha maal aap key paas ley aaya, to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney puchha : '' apney ghar walon key liye kya chhoda hai? ''main ney arz kya : itna hi (unkey liye bhi chhoda hun) aur abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) wo sab maal ley aaye jo unkey paas tha, to aap ney puchha : '' abu-Bakar ! apney ghar walon key liye kya chhoda hai?'' to unhoney arz kya : unkey liye to Allah aur uskey Rasool ko chhod kar aaya hun, mainey (apney ji mein) kaha : Allah ki qasam! main un sey kabhi bhi aagey nahin badh sakunga. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3676,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas eik aurat ney aa kar kisi masley mein aap sey baat ki aur aap ney isey kisi baat ka hukm diya to wo boli : mujhey bataiye Allah key Rasool! agar main aap ko na paaon? (to kis key paas jaaun) aap ney farmaya : ''agar tum mujhey na paana to abu-Bakar key paas jana''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey sahih gharib hai.
3677,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''us doran ke eik shakhs eik gaey par sawar tha achcha wo gaey bol padi ke main uskey liye nahin paida ki gaee hun, main to khet jotney key liye paida ki gaee hun (ye keh kar) Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''mera is par eman hai aur abu-Bakar o umr ka bhi, abu-Salma kehtey hain : halanke wo dono us din wahan logon mein mojud nahin they'', wallahu aa'lam."
3678,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney (masjid ki taraf khulney waley) sarey darwazon ko band karney ka hukm diya siwaye abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key darwazey key. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai padhi. 2- is bab mein abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
3679,"abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaye to aap ney farmaya : '' tum jahannam sey Allah key azad karda ho to isi din sey unka naam Ateeq rakh diya gaya ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- baaz raawiyon ney ye hadees maan sey riwayat ki hai aur sanad mein (عن موسى بن طلحة an عائشة ) kaha hai."
3680,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''koi Nabi aisa nahin jis key do wazir aasman walon mein sey na hon aur do wazir zamin walon mein sey na hon, rahey merey do wazir aasman walon mein sey to wo Jibreel aur mekael alehissalam hain aur zamin walon mein sey merey do wazir abu-Bakar aur umr Raziallahu anhuma hain ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- aur abul-Juhaf ka naam Dawud bin Abu-Auf hai, Sufiyan Sory sey riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain : hum sey Abul-Juhaf ney bayan kya (aur wo eik pasandida shakhs they) 3- aur Talid bin Suleman (Alaihissalam) ki kunniyat abu-Idrees hai aur ye ehale-Tashayyo mein sey hain padhi. ."
3681,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aey Allah! un dono yani abu-Jahal aur umr bin Khattab mein sey jo tujhey mehbub ho uskey zariey Islam ko taqat o quwat ata farma'', aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tu un dono mein sey umr Allah key mehbub nikley''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
3682,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah Taala ney umr ki zaban o dil par haq ko jari farma diya hai ''. Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma kehtey hain : kabhi koi aisa waqia nahin huwa jis mein logon ney apni raeyn pesh kin hun aur umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ney ( Raavi khaarija ko shak ho gaya hai) bhi raey di ho, magar Quran us waqiey sey mutalliq umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki apni raey key muwaafiq na utra ho. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai, 2- khaarija bin Abdullah Ansari ka pura naam khaarija bin Abdullah bin Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Zaid bin Sabit hai aur ye Suqa hain, padhi. 3- is bab mein Fazal bin Abbas, Abu-Zar aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
3683,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aey Allah ! Islam ko abu-Jahal bin Hisham ya umr key zariey quwat ata farma '' , phir subh hui to umr Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas gaey aur Islam ley aaye . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai, 2- baaz muhaddeseen ney nazar abu-Umar key silsiley mein unkey hifz key talluq sey kalam kya hai aur ye munkar hadisein riwayat kartey hain. ( lekin hadees raqam : (3690) sey uskey mazmoon ki taeed hoti hai) ."
3684,"umr ney abu-Bakar Raziallahu anhuma sey kaha : aey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key baad sab sey behtar insan ! is par abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : suno ! agar tum aisa keh rahey ho to mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna hai : umr sey behtar kisi aadmi par suraj tulu nahin huwa . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain, aur iski sanad qawi nahin hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
3685,mein kisi ko nahin samajhta ke wo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey mohabbat karta ho aur wo abu-Bakar o umr Raziallahu anhuma key andar kamiyan nikaley. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai.
3686,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' agar merey baad koi Nabi hota to wo umr bin Khattab hotey '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf Mushrah bin Ha-aan ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
3687,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main ney khuwab mein dekha goya mujhey doodh ka koi piyala diya gaya jis mein sey mainey kuch piya phir mainey apna bacha huwa hissa umr bin Khattab ko dey diya '' , to log kehney lagey Allah key Rasool ! aap ney uski kya tabeer ki ? aap ney farmaya : '' uski tabeer ilm hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
3688,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main jannat key andar gaya to kya dekhta hun ke main eik soney key mehal mein hun, mainey puchha : ye mehal kiska hai? farishton ney kaha : Quraish key eik nojawan ka hai, to mainey socha ke wo main hi hunga , chunanche mainey puchha ke wo nojawan kon hai? to unhoney kaha : wo umr bin Khattab hain'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3689,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney (eik din ( subh ki to Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko bulaya aur puchha : '' Bilal ! kya wajeh hai ke tum jannat mein merey aagey aagey rahey ? kabhi aisa nahin huwa ke main jannat mein dakhil huwa hun aur apney aagey tumhari khadaaun ki aawaz na suni ho, aaj raat mein jannat mein dakhil huwa to ( aaj bhi) mainey apney aagey tumharey khadaaun ki aawaz suni , phir soney key eik chokor buland mehal par sey guzra to mainey puchha ke ye mehal kis ka hai? farishton ney bayan kya ke ye eik Arab aadmi ka hai, to mainey kaha : main ( bhi) Arab hun, bataao ye kis ka hai? to unhoney kaha : ye Quraish key eik shakhs ka hai, mainey kaha : main ( bhi) quraishi hun, bataao ye mehal kis ka hai? unhoney kaha : ye Muhammad Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki ummat key eik fard ka hai, mainey kaha : main Muhammad hun, ye mehal kis ka hai? unhoney kaha : umr bin Khattab ka hai'' , Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! aisa kabhi nahin huwa ke mainey Azan di ho aur do rakatein na padhi hon aur na kabhi aisa huwa hai ke mujhey hadas laahiq huwa ho aur mainey usi waqt wuzu na kar liya ho aur ye na samjha ho ke Allah key liye merey ooper do rakatein ( wajib ( hain, is par Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' unhen dono rakaaton (ya khaslaton ( ki sey) ye martaba hasil huwa hai'' padhi. ( . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Jabir, Muaz, Anas aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi marvi hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''mainney jannat mein soney ka eik mehal dekha to mainey kaha : ye kiska hai? kaha gaya : ye umr bin Khattab ka hai'', 3- hadees key alfaz « أني دخلت البارحة الجنة » ka mafhoom ye hai ke mainey khuwab mein dekha ke goya main jannat mein dakhil huwa hun, baaz riwaayaton mein aisa hi hai, 4- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke unhoney kaha : anbiya key khuwab wahi hain."
3690,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam kisi ghazwey mein nikley, phir jab wapis aaye to eik siyah rang ki (Habshi) laundi ney aa kar kaha : Allah key Rasool ! mainey nazar maana thi ke agar Allah ney aap ko b-khair o aafiyat lotaya to main aap key samney daf bajaungi aur gaana gaaungi, to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney us sey farmaya : '' agar tu ney nazar maana thi to baja ley warna nahin '' padhi. , chunanche wo bajaney lagi, usi doran abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) andar dakhil huye aur wo bajati rahi, phir Ali (Raziallahu anhu) dakhil huye aur wo bajati rahi, phir Usman (Raziallahu anhu) dakhil huye aur wo bajati rahi, phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) dakhil huye to unhen dekh kar usney daf apni peeth key nichey dal li aur usi par beth gaee, ye dekh kar Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Umar! tum sey shetan bhi darta hai, main betha huwa tha aur wo baja rahi thi, itney mein abu-Bakar andar aaye to bhi wo bajati rahi, phir Ali andar aaye to bhi wo bajati rahi , phir Usman andar aaye to bhi wo bajati rahi , phir jab tum dakhil huye aey umr ! to usney daf phenk dali '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Barida ki riwayat sey ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Umar, Saad bin abi Waqas aur Aaisha (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
3691,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam bethey they ke itney mein hamney eik shor suna aur bachon ki aawaz suni chunanche Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam khadey ho gaey to dekha ke eik Habshi aurat nach rahi hai aur bachey usey gherey huye hain, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Aaisha ! aao, tum bhi dekh lo'', to main aai aur Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key kandhey par apni thodi rakh kar aapkey sar aur kandhey key beech sey usey dekhney lagi , phir aap ney farmaya : ''kya to abhi aasooda nahin hui? kya to abhi aasooda nahin hui? ''to mainey kaha ke abhi nahin taake main dekhun ke aap key dil mein mera kitna maqam hai? itney mein umr (Raziallahu anhu) aagey to sab log us aurat key paas sey bhag khadey huye, ye dekh kar Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main jinon aur insanon key shetanon ko dekh raha hun ke wo umr ko dekh kar bhag gaey, phir main bhi lot aai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai."
3692,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main pehla wo shakhs hunga jis sey zamin shaqq hogi , phir abu-Bakar , phir umr Raziallahu anhuma , ( sey zamin shaqq hogi ( phir main baqeea walon key paas aaun ga to wo merey sath uthaey jaeyngey, phir main Makka walon ka intizar karunga yahan tak ke mera hashr harmain key darmiyan hoga''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- aur Aasim bin umr muhaddeseen key nazdik Hafiz nahin hain."
3693,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''agli ummaton mein kuchh aisey log hotey they, jo (muhaddis) hotey they padhi. agar meri ummat mein koi aisa huwa to wo umr bin Khattab hongey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees sahih hai. 2- mujh sey Sufiyan key kisi shagrid ney bayan kiya ke Sufiyan bin Uena ney kaha : (muhaddis) wo hain jinhen Deen ki samajh ata ki gaee ho."
3694,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' tumharey paas jannat walon mein sey eik shakhs aa raha hai'' to abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aaye , phir aap ney farmaya : '' tumharey paas jannat walon mein sey eik shakhs aa raha hai'' , to umr (Raziallahu anhu) aaye . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki ye hadees gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu-Musa Ash-ari aur Jabir (Raziallauh anhum) sey ahadees aai hain."
3695,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''us doran ke eik shakhs apni bakriyan chara raha tha, eik bhediya aaya aur eik bakri pakad kar ley gaya to uska Malik aaya aur usney us sey bakri ko chin liya , to bhediya bola : darindon waley din mein jis din merey ilawa unka koi aur charwaaha nahin hoga to kaisey kerega? '' is par Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''mainey is par yaqin kya aur abu-Bakar ney aur umr ney bhi'' , abu-Salma kehtey hain : halanke wo dono us waqt wahan mojud nahin they."
3696,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam , abu-Bakar , umr , Ali , Usman , Talha , aur Zuber (Raziallauh anhum) Hira pahad padhi. par they, to wo chattan jis par ye log they hilney lagi to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Thehri reh , tujh par Nabi , Siddiq aur shaheed hain ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Usman, Saeed bin Zaid , ibne-Abbas , Sehal bin Saad , Anas bin Malik , aur Barira (Raziallauh anhum) sey ahadees aai hain."
3697,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ahad pahad par chadhey aur abu-Bakar, umr aur Usman (Raziallauh anhum) bhi to wo unkey sath hal utha, to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' thehra reh aey Uhad ! terey ooper eik Nabi eik Siddiq aur do shaheed hain'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3698,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' har Nabi ka eik rafeeq hota hai, aur merey rafeeq yani jannat mein Usman hongey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai, iski sanad qawi nahin aur ye munqataa hai."
3699,"jab Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ka muhaasra kya gaya to unhoney apney makaan key kothey sey jhank kar balwaiyon ko dekha phir kaha : main tumhen Allah ka hawala dey kar yad dilata hun : kya tum jantey ho ke Hira pahad sey jis waqt wo hila tha Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya tha ke '' Hira thehrey raho ! kyonkey tujh par eik Nabi , eik Siddiq aur eik shaheed key ilawa koi aur nahin ? '' , un logon ney kaha : haan , phir Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : main tumhen Allah ka hawala dey kar yad dilata hun, kya tumhen malum hai ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney jaish Usra ( ghazwa tabuk ( key silsiley mein farmaya tha : '' kon (us ghazwa ka ( kharch dega jo Allah key nazdik maqbool hoga (aur log us waqt pareshani aur tangi mein they ( '' to mainey ( kharch dey kar) us lashkar ko tayyar kya ? , logon ney kaha : haan , phir Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : main tumhen Allah ka wasta dey kar yad dilata hun : kya tumhen malum nahin ke Rooma kuney ka pani baghair qeemat key koi pi nahin sakta tha to mainey usey kharid kar ghani, mohtaj aur musafir sab key liye waqf kar diya? logon ney kaha : haan , hamen malum hai aur isi tarah aur bhi bahut si cheezen unhoney ginwaaein padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey yani abu-Abdur-Rehman ki riwayat sey jisey wo Usman sey riwayat kartey hain Hasan sahih gharib hai."
3700,"main Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki khidmat mein hazir huwa , aap jaishe-Usra ( ghazwa tabuk ( key saman ki logon ko targheeb dey rahey they, to Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huye aur boley : Allah key Rasool ! merey zimmey Allah ki raah mein so oont hain saaz o saman key saath, aap ney phir uski targheeb dilai , to Usman phir khadey huye aur boley : Allah key Rasool ! merey zimmey Allah ki raah mein do so oont hain saaz o saman key saath, aap ney phir usi ki targheeb di to Usman phir khadey huye aur boley Allah key Rasool ! merey zimmey Allah ki raah mein teen so oont hain saaz o saman key saath, mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko dekha aap member sey ye kehtey huye utar rahey they ke '' ab Usman par koi muaakhza nahin jo bhi karen, ab Usman par koi muaakhza nahin jo bhi karen ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai, hum isey sirf Sakan bin Mughira ki riwayat sey jantey hain, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abdur-Rehman bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
3701,"Usman (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas eik hazar Dinar ley kar aaye, (Hasan bin waqey jo Raavi hadees hain kehtey hain : dusri jagah meri kitab mein yun hai ke wo apni aasteen mein ley kar aaye), jis waqt unhoney jaish Usraa ko tayyar kiya, aur usey aap ki god mein dal diya, main Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko usey apni god mein ulat'te palat'tey dekha aur ye kehtey suna ke aaj key baad sey Usman ko koi bhi bura amal nuqsan nahin pahunchaeyga.''  aisa aap ney do baar farmaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai."
3702,"jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko baiat rizwaan padhi. ka hukm diya gaya to Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key qaasid bin kar ehale Makka key paas gaey huye they, jab aap ney logon sey baiat li, to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Usman Allah aur uskey Rasool key kaam sey gaey huye hain, phir aap ney apney dono haathon mein sey eik ko doosrey par maara to Rasulullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka haath jisey aap ney Usman key liye istimal kiya logon key haathon sey behtar tha.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
3703,"main us waqt ghar mein mojud tha jab Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ney kothey sey jhank kar unhen dekha aur kaha tha : tum merey samney apney un dono sathiyon ko laao , jinhoney merey khilaf tumhen jama kiya hai, chunanche un dono ko laya gaya goya wo dono do oont they ya do gadhey yani badey motey aur taqatwar , to Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ney unhen jhank kar dekha aur kaha : main tum sey Allah aur Islam ka wasta dey kar poochhta hun ke kya tumhen malum hai ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab Madina tashrif laye to yahan ruma kuwen key ilawa koi aur mitha pani nahin tha jisey log peetey to Rasulullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''kon ruma kuwen ko jannat mein apney liye us sey behtar chiz key iwaz kharid kar apney dol ko doosrey musalmanon key dol key barabar kar dega?''  yani apney sath doosrey musalmanon ko bhi peeney ka barabar ka haq dega, to mainey usey apney asal maal sey kharid aur aaj tum mujh hi ko uskey peeney sey rok rahey ho, yahan tak ke main samandar ka (khaara) pani pi raha hun? logon ney kaha : haan, yehi baat hai, unhoney kaha : main tum sey Allah aur Islam ka wasta dey kar poochhta hun ke masjid logon key liye tang ho gaee thi aur Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''kon aale falan ki zamin key tukdey ko apney liye jannat mein us sey behtar chiz key iwaz kharid kar usey masjid mein shamil kar dega?'' to mainey usey apney asal maal sey kharid aur aaj tum mujh hi ko is mein do rakat namaz padhney nahin dey rahey ho, logon ney kaha : haan , baat yehi hai, phir unhoney kaha : main Allah aur Islam ka wasta dey kar tum sey poochhta hun : kya tumhen malum hai ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Makka key pahad sabeer par they aur aap key sath Abu-Bakar , umr Raziallahu anhuma they aur main tha, to pahad larazne laga, yahan tak ke uskey kuchh pathar nichey khai mein girey to Rasulullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney isey apney pair sey maar kar farmaya : ''thehar aey sabeer ! terey ooper eik Nabi , eik Siddiq aur do shaheedon key siwa koi aur nahin.'' logon ney kaha : haan baat yehi hai. to unhoney kaha : Allahu-Akbar ! qism hai Rabe Kaba ki ! un logon ney merey shaheed honey ki gawahi dey di, ye jumla unhoney teen baar kaha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai aur Usman sey ye hadees is sanad key ilawa sey bhi aai hai."
3704,"muqarereen mulk Sham mein taqreer key liye khadey huye, un mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key as-haab mein sey bhi kuchh log they, phir sab sey aakhir main eik shakhs khada huwa jisey Murra bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) kaha jata tha, usney kaha : agar mainey eik hadees Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey na suni hoti to main khada na hota , phir unhoney fitnon ka zikr kiya aur bataya ke uska zuhoor qarib hai, phir eik shakhs munh par kapda daley huye guzra to Murra ney kaha : yani Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka qol naqal kiya : ''ye us din hidayat par hoga''  to main usey dekhney key liye uski taraf utha, to kya dekhta hun ke wo Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) hain, phir mainey unka munh Murra ki taraf kar key kaha : wo yehi hain, unhoney kaha : haan wo yehi hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.  2- is bab mein ibne-Umar , Abdullah bin Hawala aur Kaab bin Ujara (Raziallauh anhum) sey ahadees aai hain."
3705,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aey Usman ! shayad Allah tumhen koi kurta padhi. pahnaaey, agar log usey utaarna chahen to tum usey unkey liye na utaarnaa.''  is mein hadees ka eik taweel qissa hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
3706,"ehale Misr mein sey eik shakhs ney Baitullah ka Haj kiya to usney kuchh logon ko bethey dekha to puchha : ye kon log hain? logon ney bataya ye qabila Quraish key log hain, usney kaha : ye kon Shaikh hain? logon ney bataya ke ye ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma hain to wo unkey paas aaya aur bola : main aap sey eik chiz poochh raha hun aap mujhey bataiye , main aap sey is ghar ki hurmat ka wasta dey kar poochhta hun, kya aap ko malum hai ke Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ohad key din bhagey they? unhoney kaha : haan , phir usney kaha : kya aap ko malum hai ke wo baiate rizwaan key waqt mojud nahin they? unhoney kaha : haan , phir usney kaha : kya aap ko malum hai ke wo Badr mein mojud nahin they, tumharey unhoney kaha : haan, us Misri ney az-raah tajjub Allahu-Akbar kaha, is par ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ney us sey kaha : aao main terey sawaalon ko tum par wazeh kar dun : raha un ( Usman (ka uhud key din bhagna padhi. to to gawah reh ke Allah ney isey maaf kar diya aur bakhsh diya hai padhi. aur rahi Badr key din, un ki ghair haziri to unkey nikah mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki saahibzaadi thin aur Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un sey farmaya tha : ''tumhen us aadmi key barabar sawab aur uskey barabar maale ghanimat mein sey hissea milega, jo Badr mein hazir hoga.''  aur rahi un ki baiate rizwaan sey ghair haziri to uski wajeh ye hai ke agar Usman sey badh kar wadi Makka mein koi ba-izzat hota to Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ki jagah Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam usi ko bhejtey , Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Usman ko Makka bheja aur baiate rizwaan Usman key Makka janey key baad hui phir Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney apney daste Mubarak sey ishara kartey huye farmaya : ''ye Usman ka haath hai'' aur usey apney doosrey haath par maara aur farmaya : ''ye Usman ki taraf sey baiat hai''  to ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ney us sey kaha : ab ye jawab to apney sath leta ja. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3707,"hum Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki zindagi mein kehtey they : ''abu-Bakar , umr , aur Usman."
3708,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik fitne ka zikr kiya to farmaya : ''us fitne mein ye Usman bhi mazloom qatl kiya jaeyga''  (ye baat aap ney Usman (Raziallahu anhu) key mutalliq kahi). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai.
3709,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas eik janaza laya gaya taake aap is par namaze janaza padhen to aap ney is par namaz nahin padhi , aap sey arz kiya gaya : Allah key Rasool ! is sey pehley hamney aap ko nahin dekha ke aap ney kisi par janaze ki namaz na padhi ho? aap ney farmaya : ''ye Usman sey bughz rakhta tha, to Allah ney isey mabghooz kar diya.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 2- Memun bin Mehran key shagrid Muhammad bin Ziyada hadees mein bahut zaeef gardaaney jatey hain, aur Muhammad bin Ziyad jo Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) key shagrid hain ye Basraa hain aur Suqa hain, in ki kunniyat Abu Haris hai aur Muhammad bin Ziyad Al Haani jo abu-Umama key shagrid hain, Suqa (bharosemand) hain, un ki kunniyat abu-Sufiyaan hai, ye Shaami hain."
3710,"main Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath chala , aap ansaar key eik baagh mein dakhil huye aur apni hajat puri ki, phir aap ney mujh sey farmaya : ''abu-Musa ! tum darwaze par raho koi baghair ijazat key andar dakhil na honey paey''  phir eik shakhs ney aa kar darwaza khatkhataayaa, to mainey kaha : kon hai? unhoney kaha : abu-Bakar hun, to mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! ye abu-Bakar ijazat mang rahey hain, aap ney farmaya : ''unhen aaney do, aur unhen jannat ki basharat dey do'' ,chunanche wo andar aaye aur mainey unhen jannat ki basharat di, phir eik doosrey shakhs aaye aur unhoney darwaza khatkhataayaa , mainey kaha : kon hai? unhoney kaha : umr hun, mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! ye umr ijazat mang rahey hain, aap ney farmaya : ''un key liye darwaza khol do aur unhen jannat ki basharat dey do'' ,chunanche mainey darwaza khol diya, wo andar aagaey, aur mainey unhen jannat ki basharat dey di, phir eik teesrey shakhs aaye aur unhoney darwaza khatkhataayaa, to mainey kaha : kon hai? to unhoney kaha : Usman hun, mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! ye Usman ijazat mang rahey hain, aap ney farmaya : ''un key liye bhi darwaza khol do aur unhen bhi jannat ki basharat dey do, sath hi eik aazmaaish ki jo unhen pahunch kar rahegi.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye hadees dusri sanadon sey bhi abu-Usman Nahdi sey aai hai. 3- is bab mein Jabir aur ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
3711,"Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ney mujh sey jis din wo ghar mein ghire they kaha : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujh sey ehad liya tha aur main us ehad par sabir yani qaaim hun. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, hum isey sirf Ismail bin abi Khalid ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
3712,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik sariya (lashkar) rawana kiya aur us lashkar ka ameer Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko muqarrar kiya, chunanche wo us sariya (lashkar) mein gaey, phir eik laundi sey unhoney jima (samhog) kar liya padhi. logon ney un par nakeer ki aur Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key as-haab mein sey chaar aadmiyon ney tey kiya aur kaha ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey jab hum milengey to Ali ney jo kuch kiya hai usey hum aap ko bataeyngey, aur musalman jab safar sey laut'tey to pehley Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey miltey aur aap ko salam kartey they, phir apney gharon ko jatey, chunanche jab ye sariya wapis lot kar aaya aur logon ney aap ko salam kiya to un chaaron mein sey eik shakhs khada huwa aur usney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! kya aap ko malum nahin ke Ali ney aisa aisa kiya hai? to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney us sey munh pher liya, phir doosra khada huwa to doosrey ney bhi wohi baat kahi jo pehley ney kahi thi to aap ney us sey bhi munh pher liya, phir teesra shakhs khada huwa usney bhi wohi baat kahi , to us sey bhi aap ney munh pher liya, phir chautha shakhs khada huwa to usney bhi wohi baat kahi jo un logon ney kahi thi to Rasulullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam uski taraf mutawajjeh huye aur aap key chehrey sey narazagi zahir thi. aap ney farmaya : ''tum log Ali key silsiley mein kya chahtey ho? tum log Ali key silsiley mein kya chahtey ho? Ali mujh sey hain aur main Ali sey hon padhi. aur wo dost hain har us momin ka jo merey baad aayega.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf Jaafar bin Suleman (Alaihissalam) ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
3713,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jis ka main dost hun Ali bhi uskey dost hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- Shoba ney ye hadees Memun abu-Adbullah sey aur Memun ney Zaid bin Arqam sey , unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kiya hai, aur abu-Sareeha Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key Sahabi Huzefa bin Usaid Ghifaari hain."
3714,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah abu-Bakar par reham farmaaey, unhoney apni ladki sey meri shaadi kar di aur mujhey Madina ley kar aaye aur Bilal ko apney maal sey (kharid kar) azad kiya, Allah Taala umr par reham farmaai wo haq baat kehtey hain, agar-che wo kadwi ho, haq ney unhen aisey haal mein chhoda hai ke (Allah aur uskey Rasool key ilawa) unka koi dost nahin, Allah Usman par reham karey un sey farishtey bhi hayaa kartey hain, Allah Ali par reham farmaai , aey Allah ! haq ko unkey sath pher jahan wo phiren.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 2- Mukhtaar bin Nafey Kasir aur Basraa Shaikh hain. 3- abu-Hayyaan Taimi ka naam Yahya bin Saeed bin Hayyan Taimi hai aur ye Koofi hain aur Suqa (bharosemand) hain."
3715,"hum sey Ali bin Abu-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ney « رحبیہ » (makhsus baithak) mein bayan kiya, Hudebiya key din mushrekin mein sey kuchh log hamari taraf nikley , un mein Suhel bin Amr aur mushrekin key kuchh aur sardar bhi they ye sab aa kar kehney lagey : Allah key Rasool ! hamarey beton , bhaiyon aur ghulamon mein sey kuchh aap ki taraf nikal kar aagey hain, unhen Deen ki samajh nahin wo hamarey maal aur saamaanon key darmiyan sey bhag aaye hain, aap unhen wapis kar dijiye agar unhen Deen ki samajh nahin to hum unhen samjha dengey, to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aey giroh Quraish ! tum apni nafsaaniyat sey baaz aa jaao warna Allah Taala tumharey ooper aisey shakhs ko bhejeyga jo tumhari gardanen isi Deen ki khatir talwaar sey udaaeyga, Allah ney uskey dil ko eman key liye janch liya hai, logon ney arz kiya : wo kon shakhs hai? Allah key Rasool ! aur aap sey abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney bhi puchha : wo kon hai Allah key Rasool? aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney bhi ke wo kon hai Allah key Rasool? aap ney farmaya : '' wo jooti taankne wala hai, aur aap ney Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko apna joota dey rakha tha, wo usey taank rahey they, (Raavi kehtey hain) phir Ali (Raziallahu anhu) hamari janib mutawajjeh huye aur kaha : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya hai : ''jo merey ooper jhoot baandhey usey chahiye ke apna thikaana jahannam ko bana ley.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, hum isey is sanad sey sirf Rabee hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain jisey wo Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kartey hain. 2- mainey Jarood sey suna wo keh rahey they : mainey Wakee ko kehtey huye suna ke Rabaee bin Haraash ney Islam mein kabhi koi jhoot nahin bola. 3- aur mujhey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ney khabar di aur wo Abdullah bin abi Aswad sey riwayat kar rahey they, wo kehtey hain : mainey Abdur-Rehman bin Mehdi ko kehtey suna : Mansoor bin Moa'tamir ehle-koofa mein sab sey Suqa (bharosemand) aadmi hain."
3716,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Ali sey farmaya : ''tum mujh sey ho aur main tum sey hon aur is hadees main eik waqia hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
3717,"hum giroh ansaar, munafiqon ko Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey unkey bughz rakhney ki wajeh sey khub pehchantey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf Abu Haarun ki riwayat sey jantey hain aur Shoba ney Abu Haarun key silsiley mein kalam kiya hai. 2- ye hadees Aamash sey bhi riwayat ki gaee hai, jisey unhoney abu-Saaleh sey aur abu-Saaleh ney abu Saeed Khudri sey riwayat ki hai."
3718,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah ney mujhey chaar shakhson sey mohabbat ka hukm diya hai, aur mujhey bataya hai ke wo bhi un sey mohabbat karta hai.''  arz kiya gaya : Allah key Rasool ! hamen unka naam bata dijiye, aap ney farmaya : ''Ali unhi mein sey hain'' ,aap is jumle ko teen baar dohra rahey they.  aur baqi teen : Abu-Zar, Miqdaad aur Salman hain, mujhey Allah ney un logon sey mohabbat karney ka hukm diya hai, aur mujhey usney bataya hai ke wo bhi un logon sey mohabbat rakhta hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf Shareek ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
3719,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Ali mujh sey hain aur main Ali sey hon aur meri janib sey ehad todne ki baat merey ya Ali key ilawa koi aur ada nahin kerega.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai.
3720,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney apney as-haab key darmiyan bahami (aapsi) bhai chaaraa karaya to Ali (Raziallahu anhu) rotey huye aaye aur kaha : Allah key Rasool ! aap ney apney as-haab key darmiyan bhai chaaraa karaya hai aur meri bhai-chaargi kisi sey nahin karaai? to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un sey farmaya : ''tum merey bhai ho duniya aur aakhirat dono mein.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Zaid bin abi Aufi sey bhi riwayat hai,"
3721,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas eik perinda tha, aap ney dua farmaee ke ''aey lillah ! merey paas eik aisey shakhs ko ley aa jo teri makhluq mein mujhey sab sey ziyada mehbub hota ke wo merey sath is perinde ka gosht khaye, to Ali aaye aur unhoney aap key sath khana khaya.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey Suddi ki riwayat sey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 2- ye hadees Anas sey dusri sanadon sey bhi aai hai. 3- Esa bin umr Koofi hain. 4- aur Suddi ka naam Ismail bin Abdur-Rehman hai, aur unka samaa, Anas bin Malik sey hai, aur Husain bin Ali ne dekha bhi hai. Shoba , Sufiyan Sory aur zyada ney un ki tosiq ki hai, neez (isi ke saath) Yahya bin Saeed Al Qataan ney bhi unhen Suqa (bharosemand) kaha hai."
3722,jab bhi main Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey maangta to aap mujhey detey they aur jab main chup rehta to khud hi pehal kartey'' (deney mein ya bolney mein). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai.
3723,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main hikmat ka ghar hun aur Ali uska darwaza hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib, aur munkir hai. 2- baaz raawiyon ney is hadees ko Shareek sey riwayat kiya hai, aur unhoney is mein Sunabihi key waste ka zikr nahin kiya hai, aur hum nahin jantey ke ye hadees kisi Suqa (bharosemand) Raavi key wastey sey Shareek sey aai ho, is baab mein ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai,"
3724,"Muawiya bin Abi Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) ney in ko Ameer banaya to puchha ke tum Abu-Turaab (Ali) ko bura bhala kyon nahin kehtey? unhoney kaha : jab tak mujhey wo teen baaten yad rahengi jinhen Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya hai main unhen hergiz bura nahin keh sakta, aur un mein sey eik ka bhi merey liye hona mujhey is baat sey ziyada mehbub hai ke merey liye surkh oont hon, mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey farmatey huye suna hai (aap ney unhen apney kisi ghazwe mein Madine mein apna jaa-nashin muqarrar kiya tha to aap sey Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha tha : Allah key Rasool ! aap mujhey aurton aur bachon key sath chhodey ja rahey hain), to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un sey farmaya : ''kya tumhen ye pasand nahin ke tum merey liye isi tarah ho jis tarah Harun Musa key liye they, magar farq sirf itna hai ke merey baad nabuwat nahin.''  aur dusri ye ke mainey aap ko khaibar key din farmatey huye suna ke aaj mein parcham eik aisey shakhs key haath mein dunga jo Allah aur uskey Rasool sey mohabbat karta hai aur us sey Allah aur uskey Rasool bhi mohabbat kartey hain, Saad bin Abi Waqas kehtey hain to hum sab ney uskey liye apni gardanen buland kin, yani hum sab ko uski khahish hui, aap ney farmaya : ''Ali ko bulaao'' ,chunanche wo aap key paas aaye aur unhen aashoob chashm (aankh dukhne) ki shikayat thi to aap ney apna lu'aab Mubarak un ki aankh mein lagaya aur parcham unhen dey diya chunanche Allah ney unhen Fateh di, teesri baat ye hai ke jab aayate-karima « ندع أبناءنا وأبناءكم ونساءنا ونساءكم » utri. to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Ali , Fatima , Hasan aur Husain (Raziallauh anhum) ko bulaya aur farmaya : ''aey Allah ! ye merey ehal hain.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai."
3725,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney do lashkar bhejey aur un dono mein sey eik ka Ameer Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ko aur doosrey ka Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) ko banaya aur farmaya : ''jab ladaai ho to Ali Ameer rahengey chunanche Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney eik qilaa Fateh kiya aur us sey (maale ghanimat mein sey) eik laundi ley li, to merey sath Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko eik khat likh kar bheja jis mein wo aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki shikayat kar rahey they, wo kehtey hain : chunanche main Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaya aap ney khat padha to aap ka rang mutghaiyar ho gaya phir aap ney farmaya : ''tum kya chahtey ho eik aisey shakhs key silsiley mein jo Allah aur uskey Rasool sey mohabbat rakhta hai aur Allah aur uskey Rasool us sey mohabbat kartey hain.''  wo kehtey hain : mainey arz kiya : main Allah aur uskey Rasool key ghazab sey Allah ki panah chahta hun, main to sirf eik qaasid hun, phir aap khamosh ho gaey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
3726,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney ghazwaae Taaif key din Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko bulaya aur un sey sargoshi key andaz mein kuchh baaten kin, log kehney lagey : aap ney apney chacha zaad bhai key sath badi der tak sargoshi ki hai, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main ney un sey sargoshi nahin ki hai balke Allah ney un sey sargoshi ki hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf Ajlah ki riwayat sey jantey hain, aur isey ibne Fuzel key ilawa doosrey raawiyon ney bhi Ajlah sey riwayat kiya hai. 2- aap key qol ''balke Allah ney un sey sargoshi ki hai'' ka matlab ye hai ke Allah ney mujhey unkey sath sargoshi ka hukm diya hai."
3727,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey farmaya : ''Ali ! merey aur tumharey ilawa kisi key liye jayez nahin ke wo is masjid mein junbi (sambhog ke bad naapaki ki haalat mein) rahey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 2- Ali bin Munzir kehtey hain : mainey Zaraar bin Surd sey puchha : is hadees ka mafhoom kya hai? to unhoney kaha : iska matlab ye hai ke merey aur tumharey ilawa kisi key liye ye jayez nahin ke haalate janabat mein wo us masjid mein sey guzrey. 3- mujh sey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ney is hadees ko suna to wo hairat mein pad gaey."
3728,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko peer ko maboos kya gaya aur Ali ney mangal ko namaz padhi . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- aur ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf Muslim aa'war ki riwayat sey jantey hain aur Muslim aa'war muhaddeseen key nazdik qawi nahin hain, 2- isi tarah ye hadees Muslim aa'war sey bhi aai hai aur Muslim ney hiba key wastey sey isi tarah Ali sey riwayat ki hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
3729,Ali (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey they : jab bhi mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey maangta to aap mujhey detey they aur jab main chup rehta to khud hi pehal kartey ( deney mein ya bolney mein) . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai.
3730,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey farmaya : '' tum merey liye aisey hi ho jaisey Harun Musa key liye they, albatta itni baat zarur hai ke merey baad koi Nabi nahin ''. (aur Harun (Alaihissalam) Allah key Nabi they ( . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Saad , Zaid bin Arqam , Abu-Hurera aur Umme-Salma (Raziallauh anhum) sey ahadees aai hain."
3731,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey farmaya : '' tum merey liye aisey hi ho jaisey Harun , Musa key liye they, magar itni baat zarur hai ke merey baad koi Nabi nahin ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai 2- aur ye Saad bin abi Waqas key wastey sey jisey wo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kartey hain kaee sanadon sey aai hai, 3- aur Yahya bin Saeed Ansari ki sanad sey ye hadees gharib samjhi jati hai."
3732,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Ali (Raziallahu anhu) key darwazey key ilawa (masjide-nabawi mein khulney waley tamam ( darwazon ko band karney ka hukm diya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai, hum usey Shoba ki riwayat sey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
3733,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Hasan aur Husain Raziallahu anhuma ka haath pakda aur farmaya : '' jo mujh sey mohabbat karey , aur un dono sey , aur un dono key baap aur un dono ki maa sey mohabbat karey , to wo qiyamat key din merey sath merey darja mein hoga ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum usey Jaafar bin Muhammad ki riwayat sey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
3734,"pehley pehal jisney namaz padhi wo Ali (Raziallahu anhu) hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai, Shoba ki ye hadees jisey wo Abu-Balj sey riwayat kartey hain hum isey sirf Muhammad bin Humed ki riwayat sey jantey hain aur Abu-Balj ka naam Yahya bin Sulem hai, padhi. 3- ehle-ilm ney is silsiley mein ikhtilaf kya hai, baaz raawiyon ney kaha hai ke pehley pehal jisney Islam qubul kya hai wo abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) hain, aur ba'zon ney kaha hai ke pehley pehal jo Islam laye hain wo Ali (Raziallahu anhu) hain, aur baaz ehle-ilm ney kaha hai : badey mardon mein jo pehley pehal Islam laye hain wo abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) hain aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) jab Islam laye to wo aath saal ki umr key ladkey they, aur aurton mein jo sab sey pehley Islam laee hain wo khadeeja (Raziallahu Anha) hain padhi. ."
3735,jisney sab sey pehley Islam qubul kya wo Ali (Raziallahu anhu) hain. Amr bin Murra kehtey hain : mainey isey Ibrahim Nakhai sey zikr kya to unhoney uska inkar kya aur kaha : sab sey pehley jisney Islam qubul kya wo abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
3736,"Nabi ummi Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujh sey farmaya : '' tum sey sirf momin hi mohabbat karta hai aur munafiq hi bughz rakhta hai'' padhi. . Adi bin Sabit kehtey hain : main us tabqey key logon mein sey hun, jinkey liye Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney dua farmaai padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3737,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik lashkar rawana farmaya jis mein Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they, mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko suna aap apney dono haath uthaey huye ye dua farma rahey they : اللهم لا تمتني حتى تريني عليا '' aey Allah ! to mujhey maarna nahin jab tak ke mujhey Ali ko dikha na dey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
3738,"Uhud key din Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam do zirhen pehney huye they, aap eik chattan par chadhney lagey lekin chadh na sakey to apney nichey Talha ko bithaya aur chadhey yahan tak ke chattan par sidhey khadey ho gaey, to mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : '' Talha ney apney liye ( jannat ( wajib kar li '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
3739,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna hai : '' jis ko is baat sey khushi ho ke wo kisi shaheed ko) duniya hi mein) zamin par chalta huwa dekhey to usey chahiye ke wo Talha ko dekh ley '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf salat ki riwayat sey jantey hain, 2- baaz ehle-ilm ney salat bin Dinar aur Saleh bin Musa key silsiley mein un dono key hifz key talluq sey kalam kya hai."
3740,"mein Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aaya to unhoney kaha : kya main tumhen ye khushkhabri na sunaun ke mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna hai : ''Talha un logon mein sey hain jinkey silsiley mein Allah ney farmaya hai ke wo apna kaam pura kar chukey hain'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai, hum usey Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat sey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
3741,mainey Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huye suna hai ke merey kanon ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key zaban Mubarak sey suna hai aap farma rahey they : '' Talha aur Zuber dono merey jannat key padosi hain ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain.
3742,"Sahaba ney eik jahil Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) sey kaha : tum Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey (من قضى نحبه) key mutalliq poochho ke us sey kon murad hai, Sahaba ka ye haal tha ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka is qadr ehtiraam kartey they ke aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki un par itni haibat taari rehti thi ke wo aap sey sawal ki jur'at nahin kar paatey they, chunanche us Erabi (dehati) ney aap sey puchha to aap ney apna munh pher liya , usney phir puchha : aap ney phir munh pher liya phir main masjid key darwazey sey nikla , main sabz (hara) kapdey pehney huye tha, to jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujhey dekha to farmaya : ''(من قضى نحبه) key mutalliq poochhney wala kahan hai? ''ea'raab bola : main mojud hun Allah key Rasool ! aap ney farmaya : ''ye (عن قضی نحبہ) mein sey hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf abu-Kuraib ki riwayat sey jantey hain jisey wo Yunus bin Bakeer sey riwayat kartey hain. 2- bade muhaddeseen mein sey mutaaddid (bahut se) logon ney abu-Kuraib sey riwayat ki hai. 3- mainey isey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko abu-Kuraib key wastey sey bayan kartey suna hai, aur unhoney is hadees ko apni kitab ''kitab al fawaed'' main rakha hai."
3743,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Qureza key din apney maa aur baap dono ko merey liye jama kiya aur farmaya : ''merey maa baap tum par fidaa hon.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
3744,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''har Nabi key Hawaari hotey hain padhi. aur merey hawaari Zuber bin Awam hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- aur hawaari madadgar ko kaha jata hai, mainey ibne-Abi umr ko kehtey huye suna ke Sufiyan bin Uena ney kaha hai ke hawaari key maana madadgar key hain."
3745,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : ''har Nabi key hawaari hotey hain aur merey hawaari Zuber bin Awam hain.''  aur Abu Nuaim ney is mein (ghazwae ehzaab) ka izafa kiya hai, aap ney farmaya : ''kon merey paas kafiron ki khabar laayega?'' to Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) boley : main , aap ney teen baar usey puchha aur Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ney har baar kaha : main. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3746,Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ney apney betey Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma ( ko jange-jamal ki subah ko wasiyat ki aur kaha : mera koi uzu aisa nahin hai jo Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki rafaqat mein zakhmi na huwa ho yahan tak ke meri sharmgaah bhi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Hammad bin Zaid ki riwayat sey ye hadees Hasan gharib hai.
3747,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' abu-Bakar jannati hain, umr jannati hain, Usman jannati hain, Ali jannati hain, Talha jannati hain, Zuber jannati hain, Abdur-Rehman bin Auf jannati hain, Saad jannati hain, Saeed (Saeed bin Zaid) jannati hain aur abu-Ubaida bin Jarrah jannati hain.'' Abu-Musab ney hamein khabar di ke unhoney Abdul-Azeez bin Muhammad key aagey padha aur Abdul-Azeez ney Abdur-Rehman bin Humed sey aur Abdur-Rehman ney apney walid Humed key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi tarah ki hadees riwayat ki lekin is mein Abdur-Rehman bin Auf key waste ka zikr nahin hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Abdur-Rehman bin Humed sey ba-tareeq : « an Abeeh an Saeed bin Zaid  an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam » bhi aai hai, (aur isi tarah aai hai), aur ye pehli hadees sey ziyada sahih hai (jo aagey aa rahi hai)."
3748,"Saeed bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ney un sey kaee ashkhaas (logo) ki mojudgi mein bayan kiya ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''das aadmi jannati hain, abu-Bakar jannati hain, umr jannati hain Usman , Ali , Zuber , Talha , Abdur-Rehman , abu-Ubaida aur Saad bin abi Waqas (jannati hain).'' wo kehtey hain : to unhoney un nau (9) ko gin kar bataya aur daswen aadmi key barey mein khamosh rahey, to logon ney kaha : aey Abul-A'awar hum Allah ka wasta dey kar aap sey poochh rahey hain ke daswaan kon hai? to unhoney kaha : tum logon ney Allah ka wasta dey kar puchha hai (isliye mein bata raha hun) Abul-A'awar jannati hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey suna hai ke ye pehli hadees sey ziyada sahih hai. 2- Abul-A'awar sey murad khud Saeed bin Zaid bin Amr bin Nufail hain."
3749,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ( apni biwiyon sey) farmatey they : tum logon ka maamla mujhey pareshan kiye rehta hai ke merey baad tumhara kya hoga? tumharey huquq ki adaegi key maamle mein sirf sabr karney waley hi sabr kar sakengey. phir Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ney (abu-Salma sey) kaha : Allah tumharey walid yani Abdur-Rehman bin Auf ko jannat ki nehar salsabeel sey sairab kerey. unhoney aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki biwiyon key sath eik aisey maal key zariye jo chaalis hazar (deenar) mein bikaa, achchhey sulook ka muzahira kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
3750,Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ney Ummehaatul-Momineen (Raziallahu anhuma) key liye eik baagh ki wasiyat ki jisey chaar lakh (dirham) mein bechaa gaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai.
3751,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aey Allah ! Saad jab tujh sey dua karen to un ki dua qubul farma.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Ismail bin Abi Khalid sey Qais bin Hazim key wastey sey riwayat ki gaee hai ke Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aey Allah ! Saad jab tujh sey dua karen to un ki dua Qubul farma'' aur ye ziyada sahih hai (yani : mursal riwayat ziyada sahih hai).
3752,"Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) aaye to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''ye merey mamu hain, to mujhey dikhaye koi apna mamu.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey Mujaalid hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 2- Saad bin Abi Waqas qabila bani Zohra key eik fard they aur Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki walida mohtarma qabila bani Zohra hi ki thin, isi wajeh sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya ke ''ye merey mamu hain''."
3753,"un dono ney Saeed bin Musaiyab ko kehtey huye suna ke Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Saad key ilawa kisi aur key liye apney baap aur maa ko jama nahin kiya, ohad key din aap ney Saad sey farmaya : ''tum teer maaro merey baap aur maa tum par fidaa hon, tum teer maaro aey jawan patthey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye hadees mutaaddid (bahut se) logon sey riwayat ki gaee hai in sab ney isey Yahya bin Saeed sey , aur Yahya ney Saeed bin Musaiyab key wastey sey Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat ki hai."
3754,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney ohad key din apney maa aur baap dono ko merey liye jama kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye hadees Abdullah bin Shaddad bin Haad sey bhi riwayat ki gaee hai aur unhoney Ali bin Abi Talib key wastey sey Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai.
3755,"Mainey Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey apney baap aur maa ko Saad key ilawa kisi aur par fidaa kartey nahin suna, mainey ohad key din aap ko farmatey huye suna : ''Saad tum teer maaro, merey baap aur maa tum par fidaa hon.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees sahih hai."
3756,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko kisi ghazwe sey Madina wapis aaney par eik raat neend nahin aai, to aap ney farmaya : ''kash koi mard Saleh hota jo aaj raat meri nigehbani karta'' ,hum isi khayal mein they ke hamney hathiyaron key khankhnahat ki aawaz suni, to aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney puchha : ''ye kon hai?'' aaney waley ney kaha : main Saad bin abi Waqas hun, to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un sey puchha : tum kyon aaye ho? to Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : merey dil mein ye andesha paida huwa ke kahin Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko koi nuqsan na pahunchey isliye main aap ki nigehbani key liye aaya hun, to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney unkey liye dua farmaee phir so gaey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3757,"main nau ashkhaas (logon) key silsiley mein is baat ki gawahi deta hun ke ye log jannati hain aur agar main daswen key silsiley mein gawahi dun to bhi gunehgar nahin hunga, aap sey kaha gaya : ye kaisey hai? (zara iski wazahat keejiye) to unhoney kaha : hum Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath hira pahad par they to aap ney farmaya : ''thehra reh aey hiraa ! terey ooper eik Nabi, ya Siddiq, ya shaheed padhi. key ilawa koi aur nahin.''  arz kiya gaya : wo kon log hain jinhen aap ney Siddiq ya shaheed farmaya hai? (unhoney kaha) Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : wo abu-Bakar , umr , Usman , Ali , Talha , Zuber , Saad aur Abdur-Rehman bin Auf hain (Raziallauh anhum) , puchha gaya : daswen shakhs kon hain? to Saeed ney kaha : wo main hun. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye hadees kaee sanadon sey Saeed bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey aai hai."
3758,"Abbas bin Abdul-Muttalib Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas ghusse ki haalat mein aaye , main aap key paas betha huwa tha, aap ney puchha : ''tum ghussa kyon ho?'' wo boley : Allah key Rasool ! Quraish ko hum sey kya (dushmani) hai ke jab wo aapas mein miltey hain to khush rui sey miltey hain aur jab hum sey miltey hain to aur tarah sey miltey hain, (ye sun kar) Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ghusse mein aagey, yahan tak ke aap ka chehra surkh ho gaya, phir aap ney farmaya : ''qasam hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! kisi shakhs key dil mein eman dakhil nahin ho sakta jab tak ke wo Allah aur uskey Rasool ki khatir tum sey mohabbat na kerey.''  phir aap ney farmaya : ''aey logo ! jisney merey chacha ko aziyat pahunchaai to usney mujhey aziyat pahunchaai kyonkey aadmi ka chacha uskey baap key jaisa hota hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3759,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Abbas mujh sey hain aur main un sey hun.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, hum isey sirf Israel ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
3760,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) key silsiley mein farmaya : ''bila-shubah aadmi ka chacha uskey baap key jaisa hota hai'' umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey unkey sadqe key silsiley mein koi baat ki thi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
3761,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Abbas Allah key Rasool key chacha hain aur aadmi ka chacha uskey baap key misl (jaisa) hota hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, hum isey abu-Zinad ki riwayat sey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
3762,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey farmaya : ''do shamba ki subah ko aap apney ladkey key sath merey paas aaiye taake main aap key haq main eik aisi dua kar dun jis sey Allah aap ko aur aap key ladkey ko faaeeda pahunchaey.''  phir wo subah ko gaey aur hum bhi unkey sath gaey to aap ney hamein eik chadar udha di, phir dua ki : ''aey Allah ! Abbas ki aur unkey ladkey ki bakhshish farma, aisi bakhshish jo zahir aur baatin dono aetbar sey aisi ho ke koi gunah na chodey, aey Allah ! un ki hifazat farma, unkey ladkey key silsiley mein yani uskey huquq ki adaegi ki unhen khub tofiq marahmat farma.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
3763,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main ney Jaafar ko jannat mein farishton key sath udtey dekha hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf Abdullah bin Jaafar ki riwayat sey jantey hain, aur Yahya bin Moayan waghera ney in ko zaeef thehraya hai, aur Abdullah bin Jaafar : Ali bin Madini key walid hain. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat aai hai."
3764,na kisi ney joota pehnaya aur na pehna aur na sawar huwa sawaariyon par aur na chadha oont ki kaathi par jo Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key baad Jaafar bin abi Talib sey afzal aur behtar ho. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- « کور » key maana kajaawa key hain.
3765,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Jaafar bin Abi Talib sey farmaya : ''tum surat aur seerat dono mein merey mushabeh ho''  aur is hadees main eik qissa hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. hum sey Sufiyan bin Wakee ney bayan kiya, wo kehtey hain ke hum sey Walid ney Israel key wastey sey isi jaisi hadees riwayat ki."
3766,"main Quran ki aayaton key silsiley mein Sahaba sey puchha karta tha, chaahey main uskey barey un sey ziyada waqif hota aisa isliye karta taake wo mujhey kuchh khilaeyn, chunanche jab main Jaafar bin Abi Talib sey poochhta to wo mujhey jawab us waqt tak nahin detey jab tak mujhey apney ghar na ley jatey aur apni biwi sey ye na kehtey ke Asma hamein kuchh khilaao, phir jab wo hamein khila deten tab wo mujhey jawab detey, Jaafar (Raziallahu anhu) miskinon sey bahut mohabbat kartey they, un mein ja kar bethtey they un sey baaten kartey they, aur un ki baaten suntey they, isi liye Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam unhen Abul Masakeen kaha kartey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- Abu-Is'haq Makhzoomi ka naam Ibrahim bin Fazal Madni hai aur baaz muhaddeseen ney unkey silsiley mein unkey hifz key talluq sey kalam kiya hai aur un sey ghareeb hadisein marvi (riwayat hui) hain."
3767,"hum Jaafar bin Abi Talib ko Abul-Masakin keh kar pukartey they, chunanche jab hum unkey paas aatey to wo jo kuchh mojud hota hamarey samney la kar rakh detey, to eik din hum unkey paas aaye aur jab unhen koi chiz nahin mili, (jo hamein pesh kartey) to unhoney shehad ka eik ghada nikala aur usey toda to hum usi ko chaatney lagey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees abu-Salma ki riwayat sey jisey unhoney Abu-Hurera sey riwayat ki hai, Hasan gharib hai."
3768,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Hasan aur Husain ehale jannat key jawaanon key sardar hain.''
3769,"main eik raat kisi zarurat sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaya , aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam nikley to aap eik aisi chiz lapetey huye they jisey main nahin jaan paa raha tha ke kya hai, phir jab main apni zarurat sey farigh huwa to mainey arz kiya : ye kya hai jis ko aap lapetey huye hain? to aap ney isey khola to wo Hasan aur Husain Raziallahu anhuma they, aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key kulhe sey chipkey huye they, phir aap ney farmaya : ''ye dono merey betey aur merey nawaasey hain, aey Allah ! main in dono sey mohabbat karta hun, to bhi in sey mohabbat kar aur us sey bhi mohabbat kar jo in sey mohabbat karey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
3770,"ehale Iraaq key eik shakhs ney ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey machchhar key khoon key barey mein puchha jo kapdey mein lag jaaey ke uska kya hukm hai? padhi. to ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ney kaha : is shakhs ko dekho ye machchhar key khoon ka hukm poochh raha hai ! halanke inhin logon ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key nawaason ko qatl kiya hai, aur mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna hai : ''Hasan aur Husain Raziallahu anhuma ye dono meri duniya key phool hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees sahih hai. 2- isey Shoba aur Mehdi bin Memun ney bhi Muhammad bin abi Yaqub sey riwayat kiya hai. 3- Abu-Hurera key wastey sey bhi Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi tarah ki riwayat aai hai."
3771,"main Ummul-momenin Umme-Salma (Raziallahu Anha) key paas aai, wo ro rahi thin, mainey puchha : aap kyon ro rahi hain? wo bolin, mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko dekha hai (yani khuwab mein) aap key sar aur daadhi par mitti thi, to mainey arz kiya : aap ko kya huwa hai? Allah key Rasool ! to aap ney farmaya : ''maine Husain ka qatl abhi abhi dekha hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai."
3772,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey puchha gaya ke aap key ehale bait mein aap ko sab sey ziyada mehbub kon hain? to aap ney farmaya : ''Hasan aur Husain'' (Raziallahu anhuma), aap Fatima (Raziallahu Anha) sey farmatey : ''merey dono beton ko bulaao, phir aap unhen choomtey aur unhen apney Sina sey lagatey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Anas ki riwayat sey ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai."
3773,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney member par chadh kar farmaya : ''mera ye beta sardar hai, Allah Taala iskey zariye do badey girohon mein suleh karaaeyga.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- aur « ابني هذا » sey murad Hasan bin Ali  Raziallahu anhuma hain."
3774,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam hamein khutba dey rahey they ke achcha Hasan aur Husain Raziallahu anhuma dono surkh qamis pehney huye girtey padtey chaley aa rahey they, aap ney member sey utar kar un dono ko utha liya, aur in ko la kar apney samney bitha liya, phir farmaya : ''Allah taala ney sach farmaya hai: « إنما أموالكم وأولادكم فتنة » ''tumharey maal aur tumhari aulad tumharey liye aazmaaish hain, mainey in dono ko girtey padtey aatey huye dekha to sabr nahin kar saka, yahan tak ke apni baat rok kar mainey inhen utha liya.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf Husain bin Waqid ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
3775,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Husain mujh sey hain aur main Husain sey hon padhi. Allah us shakhs sey mohabbat karta hai jo Husain sey mohabbat karta hai, Husain qabaayel mein sey eik qabila hain.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain 1- ye hadees Hasan hai hum isey sirf Abdullah bin Usman bin Khaseem ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 2- isey Abdullah bin Usman bin Khaseem sey mutaaddid (bahut se) logon ney riwayat kiya hai."
3776,logon mein Hasan bin Ali Raziallahu anhuma sey ziyada Allah key Rasool key mushabeh koi nahin tha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
3777,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko dekha aur Hasan bin Ali Raziallahu anhuma un sey mushaabihat rakhtey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein abu-Bakar Siddiq , ibne-Abbas aur Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
3778,main Ubedullah bin Ziyad key paas tha ke Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ka sar laya gaya to wo un ki naak main apni chhadi maar kar kehney laga mainey is jaisa khoobsurat kisi ko nahin dekha kyon unka zikr husn sey kiya jata hai (jab ke wo Husain nahin hai). to mainey kaha : suno ye ehale bait mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey sab sey ziyada mushabeh they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai.
3779,"Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) seene sey sar tak key hissey mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey sab sey ziyada mushabeh they, aur Husain (Raziallahu anhu) us hissey mein jo us sey nichey ka hai sab sey ziyada Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey mushabeh they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
3780,"jab Ubedullah bin Ziyad aur uskey sathiyon key sar laye gaey padhi. aur koofa ki eik masjid mein unhen tarteeb sey rakh diya gaya aur main wahan pahuncha to log ye keh rahey they : aaya aaya , to kya dekhta hun ke eik sanp saron key beech sey ho kar aaya aur Ubedullah bin Ziyad key dono nathnon mein dakhil ho gaya aur thodi der is mein raha phir nikal kar chala gaya, yahan tak ke ghaaieb ho gaya, phir log kehney lagey : aaya aaya , is tarah do ya teen baar huwa. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3781,"mujh sey meri walida ney puchha : tum Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki khidmat mein haal hi mein kab gaey they? mainey kaha : itney itney dino sey main unkey paas nahin ja saka hun, to wo mujh par khafa huin, mainey un sey kaha : ab mujhey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas janey dijiye main aap key sath namaze maghrib padhunga aur aap sey main apney aur aap key liye duaae maghfirat ki darkhaast karunga, chunanche main Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaya aur aap key sath maghrib padhi phir aap (nawaafil) padhtey rahey yahan tak ke aap ney Isha padhi, phir aap lotey to main bhi aap key sath peechhey-peechhey chala, aap ney meri aawaz suni to farmaya : ''kon ho? Huzaifa?'' mainey arz kiya : ji haan, Huzefa hun, aap ney farmaya : « ما حاجتك غفر الله لك ولأمك » ''kya baat hai? bakhshey Allah tumhen aur tumhari maa ko'' (phir) aap ney farmaya : ''ye eik farishta tha jo us raat sey pehley zamin par kabhi nahin utra tha, usney apney Rab sey mujhey salam karney aur ye basharat deney ki ijazat maangi ke Fatima jannati aurton ki sardar hain aur Hasan aur Husain Raziallahu anhuma ehale jannat key jawaanon (yani jo duniya mein jawan they un) key sardar hain.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf Israel ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
3782,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Hasan aur Husain Raziallahu anhuma ko dekha to farmaya : « اللهم إني أحبهما فأحبهما » ''aey Allah ! main in dono sey mohabbat karta hun, to bhi in dono sey mohabbat farma.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3783,"mainey Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko dekha , aap apney kandhey par Hasan bin Ali Raziallahu anhuma ko bithaaey huye they aur farma rahey they : « اللهم إني أحبه فأحبه » ''aey Allah ! main is sey mohabbat karta hun to bhi is sey mohabbat farma.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, aur ye Fuzel bin Marzooq ki (mazkoora) riwayat sey ziyada sahih hai."
3784,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Husain bin Ali Raziallahu anhuma ko apney kandhey par uthaey huye they to eik shakhs ney kaha : betey ! kya hi achchhi sawari hai jis par to sawar hai, to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aur sawar bhi kya hi achchha hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 2- Zamaa bin Saleh ko baaz muhaddeseen ney unkey hifz key talluq sey zaeef thehraya hai."
3785,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''har Nabi ko Allah ney saat numaende inayat farmaai hain, aur mujhey chaudah.''  hamney arz kiya : wo kon log hain? aap ney farmaya : ''main , merey dono nawaasey, Jaafar, Hamza, abu-Bakar, Umar, Musab bin Umair, Bilaal, Salman, Miqdaad, Huzaifa, Ammar aur Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallauh anhum).'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai. 2- ye hadees Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey moqufan bhi aai hai."
3786,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko Hajjatul-wadaa mein Arfa key din dekha, aap apni oontni qaswaa par sawar ho kar khutba dey rahey they, mainey aap ko farmatey huye suna : ''aey logo ! main tum mein aisi chiz chhodey ja raha hun ke agar tum isey pakdey rahogey to hergiz gumrah na ho'o-gey : eik Allah ki kitab hai doosrey meri « عترت » yani ehale-bait (ghar waale) hain.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai. 2- Zaid bin Hasan sey Saeed bin Suleman (Alaihissalam) aur mutaaddid (bahut se) ehle-ilm ney riwayat ki hai. 3- is bab mein Abu-Zar , abu Saeed Khudri , Zaid bin Arqam aur Huzefa bin Usaid (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
3787,"jab aayate-karima :« إنما يريد الله ليذهب عنكم الرجس أهل البيت ويطهركم تطهيرا » ''aey Nabi ke ghar waalon ! Allah chahta hai ke tum sey (kufr aur shirk) ki gandagi door kar dey, aur tumhari khub tatheer (paak) kar dey'' (Ahzab : 33), Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam par Umme-Salma (Raziallahu Anha) key ghar mein utrin to aap ney Fatima aur Hasan aur Husain (Raziallauh anhum) ko bulaya aur aap ney unhen eik chadar mein dhanp liya aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) aap ki pusht Mubarak key peechhey they to aap ney unhen bhi chadar mein chhupa liya, phir farmaya : « اللهم هؤلاء أهل بيتي فأذهب عنهم الرجس وطهرهم تطهيرا » ''aey Allah ! ye merey ehale-bait (ghar waale) hain to in ki napaki ko door farma dey aur inhen achchhi tarah paak kar dey.'' Umme-Salma ney arz kiya : Allah key Nabi ! main bhi inhen key sath hun, aap ney farmaya : ''tu apni jagah par reh aur to bhi neki par hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Umme-Salma , Maaqil bin Yasaar, Abu Humra aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey ahadees aai hain."
3788,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main tum mein aisi chiz chhodney wala hun ke agar tum usey pakdey rahogey to hergiz gumrah na hogey : un mein sey eik doosrey sey badi hai aur wo Allah ki kitab hai goya wo eik rassi hai jo aasman sey zamin tak latki hui hai, aur dusri meri « عترت » yani merey ehale-bait (ghar waale) hain ye dono hergiz juda na hongey, yahan tak ke ye dono hoze Kausar par merey paas aayengey, to tum dekh lo ke un dono key silsiley main tum meri kaisi jaa-nasheeni kar rahey ho.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
3789,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah sey mohabbat karo kyonkey wo tumhen apni nematon khila raha hai, aur mohabbat karo mujh sey Allah ki khatir, aur merey ehale bait (ghar waalon) sey meri khatir.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
3790,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''meri ummat mein sab sey ziyada meri ummat par reham karney waley abu-Bakar hain aur Allah key maamle mein sab sey ziyada sakht umr hain, aur sab sey ziyada sachchi hayaa waley Usman bin Affaan hain, aur halal aur haram key sab sey badey jaankar Muaz bin Jabal hain, aur faraaiz (meeras) key sab sey ziyada jaan'ney waley Zaid bin Sabit hain, aur sab sey badey qaari Ubai-bin Kaab hain, aur har ummat main eik ameen hota hai aur is ummat key ameen abu-Ubaida bin Jarrah hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey is sanad sey sirf Qatada ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 2- isey abu-Qulaba ney Anas key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi key maanind riwayat kiya hai aur mashhoor abu-Qulaba wali riwayat hai,"
3791,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''meri ummat mein sab sey ziyada meri ummat par reham karney waley abu-Bakar hain aur Allah key maamle mein sab sey ziyada sakht umr hain aur sab sey ziyada sachchi hayaa waley Usman hain aur Allah ki kitab key sab sey badey qaari Ubai-bin Kaab hain aur faraaiz (meeras) key sab sey badey jaankar Zaid bin Sabit hain aur halal aur haram key sab sey badey aalim Muaz bin Jabal hain aur suno har ummat ka eik ameen hota hai aur is ummat key ameen Abu-Ubaida bin Jarrah hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
3792,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) sey farmaya : ''Allah ney mujhey hukm diya hai ke main tumhen « لم يكن الذين كفروا  padh kar sunaaun, unhoney arz kiya : kya is ney mera naam liya hai, aap ney farmaya : ''haan (ye sun kar) wo ro padey.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain : Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujh sey farmaya : ''phir unhoney isi tarah ki hadees zikr ki.''"
3793,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un sey farmaya : ''Allah ney mujhey hukm diya hai ke main tumhen padh kar sunaaun.''  phir aap ney unhen (لم يكن الذين كفروا من أهل الكتاب) padh kar sunaya, aur is mein ye bhi padha (إن ذات الدين عند الله الحنيفية المسلمة لا اليهودية wala النصرانية من يعمل خيرا فلن يكفره) ''beshak Deen waali padhi. Allah key nazdik tamam deenon aur millaton sey rishta kaat kar Allah ki janib yaksu ho janey wali musalman aurat hai na ke Yahudi aur nasrani aurat jo koi neki ka kaam karey to wo hergiz uski na-qadri na karey.''  aur aap ney unkey samney ye bhi padha : (ولو أن لابن آدم واديا من مال لابتغى إليه ثانيا ولو كان له ثانيا لابتغى إليه ثالثا wala يملأ جوف ابن آدم إلا التراب ويتوب الله على من تاب )''agar ibne-Adam key paas maal ki eik wadi ho to wo dusri wadi ki khahish kerega aur agar usey dusri bhi mil jaey to wo teesri chahega, aur Adam zaade ka pet sirf khaak hi bhar sakeygi, aur jo tauba karey to Allah uski tauba qubul farmata hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye hadees is sanad key ilawa dusri sanad sey bhi aai hai. 3- isey Abdullah bin Abdur-Rehman bin Abzi ney apney walid Abdur-Rehman bin Abzi sey aur unhoney Ubai-bin Kaab sey riwayat kiya hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Ubai-bin Kaab sey farmaya : ''Allah ney mujhey hukm diya hai ke main tumharey samney Quran padhun.''  4- Qatada ney Anas sey riwayat kiya hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) sey farmaya ke ''Allah ney mujhey hukm diya hai ke main tumharey samney Quran padhun''."
3794,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key ehade Mubarak mein Quran ko chaar aadmiyon ney jama kiya aur wo sab key sab ansaar mein sey hain : Ubai-bin Kaab , Muaz bin Jabal, Zaid bin Sabit aur abu-Zaid. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3795,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''kya hi achchhey log hain abu-Bakar, Umar, abu-Ubaida bin Jarrah, Usaid bin Huzer, Sabit bin Qais bin Shamaas, Muaz bin Jabal aur Muaz bin Amr bin Jamooh'' (Raziallauh anhum). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai hum isey sirf Suhel ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
3796,"eik qom ka naaib aur sardar dono Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaye aur dono ney arz kiya : hamarey sath aap apna koi ameen rawana farmaeyn, to aap ney farmaya : ''main tumharey sath eik aisa ameen bhejun ga jo amanat ka haq ba-khoobi ada kerega.''  to uskey liye logon ki nazren uth gaeen aur phir aap ney Abu-Ubaida bin Jarrah (Raziallahu anhu) ko rawana farmaya. Raavi hadees Abu-Is'haq Sabeei kehtey hain : jab wo is hadees ko Sila sey riwayat kartey to kehtey saath (60) saal huye ye hadees mainey un sey suni thi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye hadees ibne-Umar aur Anas Raziallahu anhuma key wastey sey bhi Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey aai hai, aap ney farmaya : ''har ummat ka eik ameen hota hai aur is ummat key ameen Abu-Ubaida bin Jarrah hain.''"
3797,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jannat teen aadmiyon ki mushtaaq hai : Ali, Ammaar, aur Salman (Raziallauh anhum) ki.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf Hasan bin Saleh ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
3798,"Ammar ney aa kar Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey andar aaney ki ijazat maangi to aap ney farmaya : ''unhen ijazat dey do, marhabaa mard paak zaat aur paak sifaat ko.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3799,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Ammaar ko jab bhi do baaton key darmiyan ikhtiyar diya gaya to unhoney usi ko ikhtiyar kiya jo un dono mein sab sey behtar aur haq sey ziyada qarib hoti thi.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey Abdul-Azeez bin Siyah ki riwayat sey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain, aur ye eik Koofi Shaikh hain aur in sey logon ney riwayat ki hai, unka eik ladka tha jisey Yazeed bin Abdul-Azeez kaha jata tha, un sey Yahya bin Adam ney riwayat ki hai."
3800,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Ammaar ! tumhen eik baaghi jamaat qatl kereygi.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Alaa bin Abdur-Rehman ki riwayat sey Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Umme-Salma , Abdur-Rehman bin Amr, Abu Yosr aur Huzefa (Raziallauh anhum) se ahadees aai hain."
3801,mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : ''aasman ney kisi par saya nahin kiya aur na zamin ney apney ooper kisi ko panah di jo Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey ziyada sachcha ho.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- is bab mein Abu-Darda aur Abu-Zar sey hadisein aai hain.
3802,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aasman ney kisi par saya nahin kiya aur na zamin ney kisi ko panah di jo Abu-Zar sey. jo Esa bin Maryam key mushabeh hain. ziyada zaban ka sachcha aur uska paas aur lihaz rakhney wala ho.''  ye sun kar umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) rashk key andaz mein boley : Allah key Rasool ! kya hum ye baat unhen bata den? aap ney farmaya : ''haan, bata do.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai. 2- aur ba'zon ney is hadees ko riwayat kiya hai is mein hai ke aap ney farmaya : ''Abu-Zar zamin par Esa bin Maryam ki zaahidaana chaal chaltey hain.''"
3803,"jab logon ney Usman (Raziallahu anhu) key qatl ka irada kiya to Abdullah bin Salam Usman (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aaye , Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ney un sey kaha : tum kyon aaye ho? unhoney arz kiya : main aap ki madad key liye aaya hun to aap ney kaha : tum logon key paas jaao aur unhen merey paas aaney sey bhagaao kyonkey tumhara bahar rehna merey haq main tumharey andar rehney sey ziyada behtar hai, chunanche Abdullah bin Salam nikal kar logon key paas aaye aur un sey kaha : logo ! mera naam jahiliyat mein falan tha to Rasulullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mera naam Abdullah rakha , aur meri shaan mein Allah ki kitab ki kaee aayaten nazil huin, chunanche (وشهد شاهد من بني إسرائيل على مثله فآمن واستكبرتم إن الله لا يهدي القوم الظالمين),(قل كفى بالله شهيدا بيني وبينكم ومن عنده علم الكتاب) merey hi silsiley mein utri , Allah ki talwaar miyaan mein hai aur farishtey tumharey us shehar Madina mein jis mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam utrey tumharey hamsaaya hain, lihaza tum us shakhs key qatl mein Allah sey daro, qism Allah ki ! agar tum ney isey qatl kar diya, tum apney hamsaaya farishton ko apney paas sey bhagaa dogey , aur Allah ki talwaar ko jo miyaan mein hai bahar khinch logey , phir wo qiyamat tak miyaan mein nahin aa sakeygi to log un ki ye nasihat sun kar boley is Yahudi ko qatl karo aur Usman ko bhi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf Abdul-Malik bin Umer ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 2- Shuaib bin Safwan ney bhi hadees Abdul-Malik bin Umer sey riwayat ki hai, unhoney sanad mein (عن ابن محمد بن عبد الله بن سلام an جده عبد الله بن سلام) kaha hai."
3804,"jab Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) key marney ka waqt aaya to un sey kaha gaya : aey abu-Abdur-Rehman ! hamein kuchh wasiyat kijiye , to unhoney kaha : mujhey bithaao, phir boley : ilm aur eman dono apni jagah par qaaim hain jo unhen dhoondeyga zarur paeyga, unhoney isey teen baar kaha, phir boley : ilm ko chaar aadmiyon key paas dhoondo : Uwemir Abu-Darda key paas, Salman Faarsi key paas, Abdullah bin Masood key paas aur Abdullah bin Salam key paas, (jo Yahudi they phir Islam laye) kyonkey mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna hai ke wo un das logon mein sey hain jo jannati hain."
3805,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum un dono ki perwi karo jo merey as-haab mein sey merey baad hongey yani abu-Bakar aur umr ki, aur Ammar ki rawish par chalo , aur ibne-Masood key ehad (wasiyat) ko mazbooti sey thaamey raho.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Masood ki ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai. 2- hum isey sirf Yahya bin Salma bin Kuheil ki riwayat sey jantey hain, aur Yahya bin Salma hadees mein zaeef hain. 3- Abuz-Zaara ka naam Abdullah bin Haani hai, aur wo Abuz-Zaara jin sey Shoba, Sory aur ibn Uena ney riwayat ki hai unka naam Amr bin Amr hai, aur wo Abdullah bin Masood key shagrid Abul Aahwas key bhatijey hain."
3806,"unhoney Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke main aur merey bhai dono Yamen sey aaye to hum eik arse tak yehi samajhtey rahey ke Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ehale-bait hi key eik fard hain, kyonkey hum unhen aur un ki walida ko kasrat sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas (un key ghar mein) aatey jatey dekhtey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is sanad sey ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- Sufiyan Sory ney bhi isey Abu-Is'haq sey riwayat kiya hai."
3807,"hum Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aaye to hamney un sey kaha : aap hamein bataiye ke logon mein chaal dhaal mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey sab sey qarib kon hai ke hum uskey taur tareeqey ko apnaeyn , aur uski baaten sunen? to unhoney kaha ke logon mein chaal dhaal aur taur tareeqey mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey sab sey qarib ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) hain, yahan tak ke wo hum sey ojhal ho kar aap key ghar key andar bhi jaya kartey they, aur Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key as-haab ko jo kisi tarah ki tehreef ya bhool sey mehfooz hain ye ba-khoobii malum hai ke Umme Abd key betey yani Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) un sab mein Allah sey sab sey nazdik hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3808,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''agar main baghair mashware key un mein sey kisi ko ameer banata to Umme Abd key betey (Abdullah bin Masood) ko Ameer banata.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf Haris ki riwayat sey jantey hain jisey wo Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kartey hain."
3809,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''agar main baghair mashware key kisi ko Ameer banata to Umme Abd key betey (Abdullah bin Masood) ko Ameer banata.''
3810,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Quran Majeed chaar logon sey seekho : ibne-Masood , Ubai-bin Kaab , Muaz bin Jabal , aur Salim Mola Abi Huzefa sey.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3811,"main Madina aaya to mainey Allah sey apney liye eik Saleh hum-nasheeni paney ki dua ki, chunanche Allah ney mujhey Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hum nasheenon ki tofiq bakhshi, main unkey paas bethney laga to mainey un sey arz kiya : mainey Allah sey apney liye eik Saleh hum-nasheeni ki tofiq marahmat farmaney ki dua ki thi, chunanche mujhey aap ki hum-nasheenon ki tofiq mili hai, unhoney mujh sey puchha : tum kahan key ho? mainey arz kiya : mera talluq ehle-koofa sey hai aur main khair ki talash aur talab mein yahan aaya hun, unhoney kaha : kya tumharey yahan Saad bin Malik jinki duaaey suni jaane waali hain padhi. aur ibne-Masood jo Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key liye wuzu key pani ka intizam karney waley aur aap key khidmat-guzaar hain aur Huzefa jo aap key hamraaz hain aur Ammar jinhen Allah ney shetan sey apney Nabi ki zabani panah di hai aur Salman jo dono kitabon waley hain mojud nahin hain. Raavi hadees Qatada kehtey hain : do kitabon sey murad Injeel aur Quran hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- Khaisma ye Abdur-Rehman bin Abu Sabra key betey hain un ki nisbat unkey dada ki taraf kar di gaee hai."
3812,"logon ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! kaash! ! aap apna janashin muqarrar farma detey, aap ney farmaya : ''agar mainey apna janashin muqarrar kar diya aur tum ney uski nafarmani ki to tum azab diye jaaogey, albatta Huzefa jo kuchh tum sey kahin tum un ki tasdeeq karo.''  aur jo Abdullah (Abdullah bin Masood) padhi. tumhen padhaaein unhen padh lo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai aur ye Shareek ki riwayat sey hai."
3813,"umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney Usama bin Zaid Raziallahu anhuma key liye baitul-maal sey saadhey teen hazar ka, wazeefa muqarrar kiya, aur Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma key liye teen hazar ka to Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma ney apney baap sey arz kiya : aap ney Usama ko mujh par tarjeeh di? Allah ki qism ! wo mujh sey kisi ghazwe mein aagey nahin rahey, to unhoney kaha : isliye ke Zaid Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko tumharey baap sey aur Usama tum sey ziyada mehbub they, isliye mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key mehbub ko apney mehbub par tarjeeh di. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
3814,"hum Zaid bin Harisa ko Zaid bin Muhammad hi keh kar pukartey they yahan tak ke aayat kareema (ادعوهم لآبائهم هو أقسط عند الله) '' tum god liye logon ko unkey apney baapon key naam se pukara karo, yehi baat Allah key nazdik ziyada  insaf ke mutabiq baat hai'' (Ahzab- 5), nazil hui. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees sahih hai."
3815,"main Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaya aur mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! merey bhai Zaid ko merey sath bhej dijiye , aap ney farmaya : ''wo mojud hain agar tumharey sath jana chah rahey hain to main unhen nahin rokoonga''  ye sun kar Zaid ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! qism Allah ki ! main aap key muqable mein kisi aur ko ikhtiyar nahin kar sakta, jabla kehtey hain : to mainey dekha ke merey bhai ki raey meri raey sey afzal thi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf ibne Romi ki riwayat sey jantey hain, jisey wo Ali bin Mus'hir sey riwayat kartey hain."
3816,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik lashkar rawana farmaya aur uska Ameer Usama bin Zaid ko banaya to log un ki amaarat par tanqeed karney lagey chunanche Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''agar tum un ki amaarat mein ta'ana kartey ho to is sey pehley unkey baap ki amaarat par bhi ta'ana kar chukey ho, qism Allah ki ! wo (Zaid) amaarat key mustahiq they aur wo mujhey logon mein sab sey ziyada mehbub they, aur unkey baad ye bhi (Usama) logon mein mujhey sab sey ziyada mehbub hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3817,"jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki bimari shadeed ho gaee to main (jurf sey) utar kar Madina aaya aur (merey sath) kuchh aur log bhi aaye , main Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas andar gaya to aap ki zaban band ho chuki thi, phir uskey baad aap kuchh nahin boley, aap apney dono haath merey ooper rakhtey aur uthatey they to main yehi samajh raha tha ke aap merey liye dua farma rahey hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
3818,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Usama ki naak poochhney ka irada farmaya padhi. to mainey kaha : aap choden main saaf kiye deti hun, aap ney farmaya : ''Aaisha ! tum is sey mohabbat karo kyonkey main is sey mohabbat karta hun.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
3819,"main Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas betha huwa tha, itney mein Ali aur Abbas Raziallahu anhuma dono andar aaney ki ijazat maangney lagey , unhoney kaha : Usama ! hamarey liye Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ijazat maango , to mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! Ali aur Abbas dono andar aaney ki ijazat mang rahey hain, aap ney farmaya : ''kya tumhen malum hai ke wo kyon aaye hain?'' mainey arz kiya : main nahin janta , is par Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''mujhey to malum hai'' ,phir aap ney unhen ijazat dey di wo andar aaye aur arz kiya ke hum aap key paas isliye aaye hain taake hum aap sey poochhen ke aap key ehal (ghar walon) mein aap ko sab sey ziyada mehbub kon hai? aap ney farmaya : ''Fatima binte Muhammad'' ,to wo dono boley : hum aap ki aulad key mutalliq nahin poochhtey hain, aap ney farmaya : ''merey ghar walon mein mujhey sab sey ziyada mehbub wo hai jis par Allah ney inaam kiya aur mainey inaam kiya hai, aur wo Usama bin Zaid hain.''  wo dono boley : phir kon? aap ney farmaya : ''phir Ali bin abi Talib hain'' ,Abbas boley : Allah key Rasool ! aap ney apney chacha ko peechhey kar diya, aap ney farmaya : ''Ali ney tum sey pehley hijrat ki hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Shoba : umr bin abi Salma ko zaeef qarar detey they."
3820,jab sey main Islam laya hun Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujhey (ijazat maangney par andar dakhil honey sey) mana nahin farmaya padhi. aur jab bhi aap ney mujhey dekha aap muskuraaey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
3821,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney jab sey mein Islam laya hun mujhey (andar janey sey) mana nahin kiya aur jab bhi aap ney mujhey dekha aap muskuraaey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
3822,"unhoney Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ko do baar dekha aur Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney unkey liye do martaba duayen kin. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees mursal hai, hamein nahin malum ke Abu Jehzam ka ibne-Abbas sey samaa (sun'na), hai ya nahin 2- ye hadees Ubedullah bin Abdullah bin Abbas sey bhi ibne-Abbas key wastey sey aai hai. 3- aur Abu Jehzam ka naam Musa bin Salim hai."
3823,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney do baar mujhey hikmat sey nawazey janey ki dua farmaae. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Ata ki riwayat sey gharib hai aur isey Ikrima ney ibne-Abbas sey riwayat kiya hai.
3824,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujhey apney seeney sey laga kar farmaya : « اللهم علمه الحكمة » ''aey Allah ! isey hikmat sikha dey.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
3825,"mainey khuwab mein dekha goya merey haath mein motey resham ka eik tukda hai aur us sey mein jannat ki jis jagah ki janib ishara karta hun to wo mujhey uda kar wahan pahuncha deta hai, to mainey ye khuwab (ummul-momenin ( Hafsa (Raziallahu Anha) sey bayan kiya phir Hafsa (Raziallahu Anha) ney isey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey bayan kiya to aap ney farmaya : ''tera bhai eik mard Saleh hai'' ya farmaya : ''Abdullah mard Saleh hain''. Imam Tirmizi : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3826,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney (khuwab mein) Zuber key ghar main eik chiragh dekha to aap ney Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey farmaya : ''Aaisha ! main yehi samjha hun ke Asma key yahan wiladat honey wali hai, to uska naam tum log na rakhna, main rakhunga''  to aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney unka naam Abdullah rakha , aur apney haath sey eik khajoor key zariey un ki tehreek (ghaati) ki. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
3827,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam guzrey to meri maa Umme Sulem ney aap ki aawaz sun kar bolen : merey baap aur meri maa aap par fidaa hon Allah key Rasool ! ye Unais padhi. hai, to Rasulullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney merey liye teen duayen kin, un mein sey do ko to mainey duniya hi mein dekh liya padhi. aur teesrey ka aakhirat mein umeedwar hun. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- ye hadees Anas sey dusri sanadon sey bhi aai hai, aur wo isey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kartey hain."
3828,kabhi kabhi Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam mujhey kehtey : ''aey do kanon wale.'' abu-Usaama kehtey hain : yani aap un sey ye mazaq key tor par farmatey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib sahih hai.
3829,"unhoney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! Anas aap ka khaadim hai, aap Allah sey uskey liye dua farma dijiye. aap ney farmaya : (اللهم أكثر ماله وولده وبارك له فيما أعطيته) ''aey Allah ! iskey maal aur aulad mein ziyadti ata farma aur jo tu ney isey ata kiya hai is mein barkat dey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3830,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney meri kunniyat eik ساگ (ghaas) key sath rakhi jisey main chun raha tha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, is hadees ko hum sirf Jabir Jaafi ki riwayat sey jantey hain jisey wo Abu Nasar sey riwayat kartey hain. 2- Abu Nasar ka naam khaisma bin Abi Khaisma Basraa hai, unhoney Anas sey kaee hadisein riwayat ki hain."
3831,"mujh sey Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : aey Sabit mujh sey ilme Deen hasil karo kyonkey uskey liye tum mujh sey ziyada moatabar aadmi kisi ko nahin paaogey, mainey isey (baraahe-raast) Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey liya hai, aur aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Jibreel (Alaihissalam) sey aur Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ney Allah Taala sey liya hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf Zaid bin Hubaab ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
3832,"Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey Ibrahim bin Yaqub wali hadees hi ki tarah hadees marvi hai, lekin is mein iska zikr nahin hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney isey Jibreel sey liya hai."
3833,"mainey Abul-Aaliya sey puchha : kya Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko suna hai? to unhoney kaha : Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki das saal khidmat ki hai aur aap ney unkey liye dua farmaee hai, aur Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ka eik baagh tha jo saal mein do baar phaltaa tha, aur us main eik khushbudar paudhaa tha jis sey mushk ki boo aati thi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- Abu Khalda ka naam Khalid bin Dinar hai aur wo muhaddeseen key nazdik Suqa (bharosemand) hain aur Abu Khalda ney Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ka zamana paya hai, aur unhoney un sey riwayat ki hai."
3834,"main Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki khidmat mein hazir huwa to mainey aap key paas apni chadar phela di, aap ney isey uthaya aur samet kar usey merey dil par rakh diya, iskey baad sey main koi chiz nahin bhoolaa. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai."
3835,"mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! main bahut si cheezen aap sey sunta hun lekin unhen yad nahin rakh paata , aap ney farmaya : ''apni chadar phailao''  to mainey usey phela diya, phir aap ney bahut sey hadisein bayan farmaeyn, to aap ney jitni bhi hadisein mujh sey bayan farmaeen main un mein sey koi bhi nahin bhoolaa. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaee sanadon sey aai hai."
3836,unhoney Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : Abu-Hurera ! aap hum sey ziyada Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki khidmat mein hazir rehney waley aur hum sey ziyada aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki hadisein yad rakhney waley hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai.
3837,"eik shakhs ney Talha bin Ubedullah key paas aa kar kaha : aey abu Muhammad ! kya ye Yamni shakhs yani Abu-Hurera Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki hadeeson ka aap logon sey ziyada jaankar hai, hum is sey aisi hadisein suntey hain jo aap sey nahin suntey ya wo Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam par aisi baat ghad kar kehta hai jo aap ney nahin farmaee, to unhoney kaha : nahin aisi baat nahin, waqae Abu-Hurera ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey aisi cheezen suni hain jo hamney aap sey nahin sunin aur uski wajeh ye thi ke wo miskeen they, unkey paas koi chiz nahin thi wo Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key mehman rehtey they, unka haath (khaney peeney mein) Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key haath key sath padta tha, aur hum gharbaar waley they aur maaldaar log they, hum Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas subah mein aur Sham hi mein aa paatey they, aur is mein koi shak nahin ke unhoney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey aisi cheezen suni hain jo hamney nahin sunin, aur tum koi aisa aadmi nahin paao gey jis mein koi khair ho aur wo Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam par jhoot baandhey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf Muhammad bin Is-haq ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 2- isey Yunus bin Bakeer ney aur unkey ilawa doosrey raawiyon ney bhi Muhammad bin Is-haq sey riwayat kiya hai."
3838,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum kis qabeele sey h?'' mainey arz kiya : main qabila dos ka hun, aap ney farmaya : ''main nahin janta tha ke dos mein koi aisa aadmi bhi hoga jis mein khair hogi.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- Abu Khalda ka naam Khalid bin Dinar hai aur Abu Aaliya ka naam Rafeea' hai."
3839,"main Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki khidmat mein kuchh khajuren ley kar hazir huwa, mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! in mein barkat ki dua farma dijiye, to aap ney unhen ikhatta kiya phir un mein barkat ki dua ki aur farmaya : ''inhen ley jaao aur apney toshae-daan mein rakh lo aur jab tum is mein sey kuchh leney ka irada karo to is mein apna haath dal kar ley lo, isey bikheron nahin chunanche hamney is mein sey itney itney wasq Allah ki raah mein diye aur hum is mein sey khatey they aur khilatey bhi they padhi. aur wo (thaili) kabhi meri kamar sey juda nahin hoti thi, yahan tak ke jis din Usman (Raziallahu anhu) qatl kiye gaey to wo toot kar (kahen) gir gaee. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai. 2- ye hadees Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey dusri sanadon sey aai hai."
3840,"mainey Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : aap ki kunniyat Abu-Hurera kyon padi? to unhoney kaha : kya tum mujh sey dartey nahin ho? mainey kaha : kyon nahin? qism Allah ki ! main aap sey darta hun, phir unhoney kaha : main apney ghar walon ki bakriyan charaataa tha, meri eik chhoti si billi thi main us ko raat main eik darkht par bitha deta aur din mein usey apney sath ley jata, aur us sey kheltaa, to logon ney meri kunniyat Abu-Hurera rakh di. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
3841,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki hadisein mujh sey ziyada kisi ko yad nahin, siwaye Abdullah bin Amr key kyonkey wo likh letey they aur main likhtaa nahin tha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3842,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) key barey mein farmaya : ''aey Allah ! to in ko hidayat dey aur hidayat yafta bana dey, aur unkey zariey logon ko hidayat dey.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
3843,"jab umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ney Umer bin Saad ko teiswin sey hataya aur un ki jagah Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ko wali banaya to logon ney kaha : unhoney Umer ko hata diya aur Muawiya ko wali banaya, to Umer ney kaha : tum log Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ka zikr bhaley tareeqe sey karo kyonkey mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna hai : « اللهم اهد به » ''aey Allah ! unkey zariye hidayat dey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- Amr bin Waqid hadees mein zaeef hain."
3844,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''log Islam laye aur Amr bin Al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) eman laye.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf ibne-Lahiaa ki riwayat sey jantey hain jisey wo Mushrah bin Haa'aan sey riwayat kartey hain aur iski sanad ziyada qawi nahin hai."
3845,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : ''Amr bin Al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) Quraish key nek logon mein sey hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is hadees ko hum sirf Nafey bin umr Jamhi ki riwayat sey jantey hain aur Nafey Suqa (bharosemand) hain aur iski sanad muttasil nahin hai, aur ibne-Abi Muleka ney Talha ko nahin paya hai."
3846,"hamney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath eik manzil par padaaw kiya, jab log aap key samney sey guzartey to aap poochhtey : ''Abu-Huraira ! ye kon hai?'' main kehta : falan hai, to aap farmatey : ''kya hi achchha banda hai ye Allah ka.''  phir aap farmatey : ''ye kon hai?'' to main kehta : falan hai to aap farmatey : ''kya hi bura banda hai ye Allah ka'' , yahan tak ke Khalid bin Waleed guzrey to aap ney farmaya : ''ye kon hai?'' mainey arz kiya : ye Khalid bin Waleed hain, aap ney farmaya : ''kya hi achchhey bandey hain Allah key Khalid bin Waleed, wo Allah ki talwaaron mein sey eik talwaar hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, aur hum nahin jantey ke Zaid bin Aslam ka samaa, Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey hai ke nahin aur ye merey nazdik mursal riwayat hai, 2- is bab mein abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
3847,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas kuchh reshmi kapdey hadiye mein aaye, un ki narmi ko dekh kar log tajjub karney lagey to Rasulullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jannat mein Saad bin Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) key roomaal is sey behtar hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se bhi hadees marvi hai."
3848,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko kehtey huye suna : aur Saad bin Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ka janaza (us waqt logon key samney rakha huwa tha). ''un key liye Rehman ka arsh (bhi khushi sey) jhoom utha.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Usaid bin Huzer, abu Saeed Khudri aur Rumaisa (Raziallauh anhum) sey ahadees aai hain."
3849,"jab Saad bin Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ka janaza uthaya gaya to munafiq kaha : kitna halka hai in ka janaza? aur ye ta'ana unhoney isliye kiya ke Saad ney bani Qureza key qatl ka faisla farmaya tha, jab Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko iski khabar hui to aap ney farmaya : ''farishtey usey uthaey huye they.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
3850,"Qais bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key liye aisey hi they jaisey Ameer (ki hifazat) key liye police wala hota hai. Raavi hadees (Muhammad bin Abdullah) Ansari kehtey hain : yani wo (aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki hifazat key liye) aap key bahut sey umoor anjam diya kartey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf Ansari ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
3851,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam merey paas aaye padhi. , aap na kisi khachchar par sawar they na Turki ghodey par. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3852,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney «ليلة البعير» (oont ki raat) mein merey liye pachchees baar duaaey maghfirat ki. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- unkey qol «ليلة البعير» oont ki raat sey wo raat murad hai jo Jabir sey kaee sanadon sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke wo eik safar mein Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath they, unhoney apna oont Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key haath bech diya aur Madina tak is par sawar ho kar janey ki shart rakh li, Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : jis raat mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key haath oont bechaa aap ney pachchees baar merey liye duaaey maghfirat farmaaee. aur Jabir key walid Abdullah bin Amr bin Haram Raziallahu anhuma Uhud key din shaheed kar diye gaey they aur unhoney kuchh ladkiyan chhodi thin, Jabir un ki parwarish kartey they aur un par kharch detey they, iski wajeh sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam unkey sath husne-suluk farmatey they aur un par reham kartey they. 3- isi tarah eik aur hadees mein Jabir sey aisey hi marvi (riwayat hui) hai."
3853,"hamney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath hijrat ki, hum Allah ki raza key chaahne wale they to hamara ajr Allah par Sabit ho gaya padhi. chunanche hum mein sey kuchh log to aisey hain ke unhoney apney ajr mein sey (duniya mein) kuchh bhi nahin khaya padhi. aur kuchh aisey hain ke unkey ummid ka darkht baar-aawar huwa aur uskey phal wo chun rahey hain, aur Musab bin Umer (Raziallahu anhu) ney aisey waqt mein intiqal kiya ke unhoney koi chiz nahin chhodi siwaye eik aisey kapdey key jis sey jab unka sar dhanpa jata to dono pair khul jatey aur jab dono pair dhaanpey jatey to sar khul jata, ye dekh kar Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''in ka sar dhanp do aur in key pairon par izkhir ghaas dal do.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3854,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''kitney bikhre hue baal ghubar-aalood aur puraney kapdey waley hain ke jinki koi parwah nahin karta aisey hain ke agar Allah key bharose par qism kha lein to Allah un ki qism ko sachi kar dey, unhi mein sey Bara bin Malik hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai."
3855,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Abu-Musa tumhen aale Dawud ki achchhi aawaazon mein sey eik achchhi aawaaz di gaee hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Barida , Abu-Hurera aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey ahadees aai hain."
3856,"hum Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath they, aap khandaq khod rahey they aur hum mitti dho rahey they, aap ney hamein dekha to farmaya : « اللهم la عيش إلا عيش الآخره فاغفر للأنصار والمهاجره » ''aey Allah zindagi to aakhirat hi ki zindagi hai, to ansaar aur muhajrin ki maghfirat farma.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Anas bin Malik sey bhi riwayat hai,"
3857,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam farmatey they : « اللهم la عيش إلا عيش الآخره فأكرم الأنصار والمهاجره » ''aey Allah zindagi to aakhirat hi ki zindagi hai, to ansaar aur muhajrin ki takrim (izzat) farma.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey ye hadees kaee sanadon sey aai hai."
3858,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : ''jahannam ki aag kisi aisey musalman ko nahin chhueygi jisney mujhey dekha, ya kisi aisey shakhs ko dekha jisney mujhey dekha hai.''  Talha (Raavi hadees) ney kaha : to mainey Jabir bin Abdullah Raziallahu anhuma ko dekha hai aur Musa ney kaha : mainey Talha ko dekha hai aur Yahya ney kaha ke mujh sey Musa (Raavi hadees) ney kaha : aur tum ney mujhey dekha hai aur hum sab Allah sey najat key umeedwar hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf Musa bin Ibrahim Ansari ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 2- is hadees ko Ali bin Madini ney aur muhaddeseen mein sey kaee aur logon ney bhi Musa sey riwayat ki hai."
3859,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''logon mein sab sey behtar mera zamana hai, phir un logon ka jo in key baad hain, phir unka jo unkey baad hain, phir unkey baad eik aisi qom aayegi jo gawahiyon sey pehley qism khayegi ya qasmon sey pehley gawahiyan degi.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein umr , Imran bin Husain aur Barida (Raziallauh anhum) sey ahadees aai hain."
3860,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jin logon ney (hudaibia mein) darkht key nichey baiat ki hai un mein sey koi bhi jahannam mein dakhil nahin hoga.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
3861,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''merey Sahaba ko bura bhala na kaho, qism hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai, agar tum mein sey koi uhad pahad key barabar bhi sona kharch karey to unkey eik mudd balke aadhey mudd key (ajr key) barabar bhi nahin pahunch sakeyga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- aap key qol «نصيفه» sey murad nisf (aadha) mudd hai."
3862,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah sey daro, Allah sey daro, merey Sahaba key mamley mein, Allah sey daro, Allah sey daro, merey Sahaba key mamley mein, aur merey baad unhen hadafe-malamat na banana, jo un sey mohabbat kerega wo mujh sey mohabbat karney ki wajeh sey un sey mohabbat kerega aur jo un sey bughz rakheyga wo mujh sey bughz ki wajeh sey un sey bughz rakheyga, jisney unhen izaa (takleef) pahunchaai usney mujhey eza (takleef) pahunchaai aur jisney mujhey eza (takleef) pahunchaai usney Allah ko eza (takleef) di, aur jisney Allah ko eza (takleef) di to qarib hai ke wo usey apni giraft mein ley ley.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum is hadees ko sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
3863,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jinhoney darkht key nichey baiat ki (yani baiate Rizwaan mein shareek rahey) wo zarur jannat mein dakhil hongey, siwaye surkh oont waley key.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
3864,"Haatib bin Abi Balta' (Raziallahu anhu) ka eik ghulam Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aa kar Haatib ki shikayat karney laga, usney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! Haatib zarur jahannam mein jaeyngey, to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum ney ghalat kaha wo is mein dakhil nahin hongey, kyonkey wo Badr aur Hudebiya dono mein mojud rahey hain.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3865,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''merey Sahaba mein sey jo bhi kisi sar zamin par mareyga to wo qiyamat key din us sar zamin walon ka peshwa aur unkey liye Noor bana kar uthaya jaeyga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- ye hadees Abdullah bin Muslim Abu-Taiba sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai aur unhoney isey Barida (Raziallahu anhu) key betey key wastey sey Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey mursalan riwayat kiya hai, aur ye ziyada sahih hai."
3866,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab tum aisey logon ko dekho jo merey as-haab ko bura bhala kehtey hon to kaho : Allah ki lanat ho tumharey shar par.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees munkir hai, hum isey Ubedullah bin umr (Umri) ki riwayat sey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain aur Nazar aur Saif dono majhool Raavi hain."
3867,"mainey Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna aur aap member par they : ''Hisham bin Mughira key beton ney mujh sey ijazat maangi hai ke wo apni beti ka nikah Ali sey kar den, to main uski ijazat nahin deta, nahin deta, nahin deta, magar ibne-Abi Talib chahen to meri beti ko Talaq dey den, aur un ki beti sey shaadi kar lein, isliye ke meri beti merey jism ka tukda hai, mujhey wo chiz buri lagti hai jo usey buri lagey aur mujhey eza (takleef) deti hai wo chiz jo usey eza (takleef) dey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- isey Amr bin Dinar ney isi tarah ibne-Abi Muleka sey aur ibne-Abi Muleka ney Miswar bin Makhrima sey riwayat kiya hai."
3868,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko aurton mein sab sey ziyada mehbub Fatima (Raziallahu anhu) thin aur mardon mein Ali (Raziallahu anhu) they, Ibrahim bin Saad kehtey hain : yani apney ehale-bait (ghar walon) mein. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
3869,"Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney Abu-Jahal ki beti ka zikr kiya to uski khabar Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko pahunchi, aap ney farmaya : ''Fatima merey jism ka tukda hai, mujhey takleef deti hai wo chiz jo usey takleef deti hai, aur ranj mein daalti hai mujhey wo chiz jo usey ranj mein daalti hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- isi tarah Ayub ney Abi Muleka sey aur unhoney ibn Zuber sey riwayat ki hai jabkey mutaaddid (bahut se) logon ney ibne-Abi Muleka key wastey sey Miswar bin Makhrima sey riwayat ki hai (jaisa ke hadees Raqam : 3880). 3- is baat ka guman hai ke ibne-Abi Muleka ney eik sath dono hi sey riwayat kiya ho (aur aisa bahut huwa hai)."
3870,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Ali, Fatima, Hasan aur Husain (Raziallauh anhum) sey farmaya : ''main ladney wala hun us sey jis sey tum lado aur suleh ka maamla karney wala hun us sey jis sey tum suleh ka maamla karo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain aur Sabeeh Mola Umme-Salma maroof (mashhur) nahin hain."
3871,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Hasan, Husain, Ali aur Fatima (Raziallauh anhum) ko eik chadar sey dhanp kar farmaya : « ‏‏‏‏اللهم هؤلاء أهل بيتي وخاصتي أذهب عنهم الرجس وطهرهم تطهيرا » ''aey Allah ! ye merey ehale bait (ghar wale) aur merey khas log hain, to in sey gandagi ko door farma dey, aur inhen achchhi tarah sey paak kar dey.''  to Umme-Salma (Raziallahu Anha) bolin : aur main bhi in key sath hun Allah key Rasool ! aap ney farmaya : ''tu (bhi) khair par hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai aur is baab mein jo hadisein marvi hain un mein sab sey achchhi hai. 2- is bab mein umr bin abi Salma , Anas bin Malik, Abul Hamraa, Maaqil bin Yasaar, aur Aaisha (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
3872,"mainey uthney bethney key taur aur tareeqe aur aadat aur khaslat mein Fatima padhi. (Raziallahu anhu) sey ziyada Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key mushabeh kisi ko nahin dekha, wo kehti hain : jab wo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaten to aap uth kar unhen bosa letey aur unhen apni jagah par bithaatey, aur jab Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam unkey paas aatey to wo uth kar aap ko bosa letin aur aap ko apni jagah par bithaatin chunanche jab Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam bimar huye to Fatima aayen aur aap par jhuken aur aap ko bosa liya, phir apna sar uthaya aur roney lagin phir aap par jhuken aur apna sar uthaya to hansney lagin, pehley to main ye khayal karti thi ke ye hum aurton mein sab sey ziyada aql wali hain magar unkey hansney par ye samjhi ke ye bhi aakhir (aam) aurat hi hain, yani ye kon sa moqey hansney ka hai, phir jab Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki wafat ho gaee to mainey un sey puchha ke ye kya baat thi ke mainey tumhen dekha ke tum Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam par jhukin phir sar uthaya to roney lagin, phir jhukin aur sar uthaya to hansney lagin, to unhoney kaha : agar aap ki zindagi mein ye baat bata deti to main eik aisi aurat hoti jo aap key raz ko faash karney wali hoti, baat ye thi ke pehley aap ney mujhey is baat ki khabar di ke is bimari mein main intiqal kar janey wala hun, ye sun kar mein ro padi, phir aap ney mujhey bataya ke unkey ghar walon mein sab sey pehley main un sey miloongi, to ye sun kar main hansney lagi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai, aur ye Aaisha sey mutaaddid (bahut se) sanadon sey aai hai."
3873,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Fateh Makka key din Fatima ko bulaya , aur un sey sargoshi ki to wo ro padin , phir dobara aap ney un sey baat ki to wo hansney lagin, unhoney bataya ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujhey ye bataya ke aap anqarib wafat paa jaeyngey, to main ro padi, phir aap ney mujhey bataya ke main Maryam binte Imran ko chhod kar ehale jannat ki tamam aurton ki sardar hongi to main hansney lagi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai."
3874,"main apney chacha key sath Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) key paas aaya to un sey puchha gaya : logon mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko sab sey ziyada mehbub kon tha? to unhoney kaha : Fatima, phir puchha gaya : mardon mein kon tha? unhoney kaha : unkey shohar, yani Ali, main khub jaanti hun wo badey rozedar aur tahajjud guzar they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- Abu Jahaaf ka naam Dawud bin Abi Auf hai, aur Sufiyan Sory sey عن ابی الجحاف key bajaey yun marvi (riwayat hui) hai : « حدثنا أبو الجحاف وكان مرضيا »."
3875,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki paak biwiyon mein sey kisi par mujhey itna rashk nahin aaya jitna Khadeeja par aaya, aur agar main in ko paa leti to mera kya haal hota? aur uski wajeh mehaz ye thi ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam unhen kasrat sey yad kartey they, agar aap bakri bhi zibeh kartey to dhoond dhoond kar khadeeja ki saheliyon ko hadiya bhejtey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
3876,"mainey kisi par itna rashk nahin kiya jitna Ummul-momenin khadeeja (Raziallahu Anha) par kiya, halanke mujh sey to aap ney nikah us waqt kiya tha jab wo intiqal kar chuki thin, aur us rashk ki wajeh ye thi ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney unhen jannat mein moti key eik aisey ghar ki basharat di thi jis mein na shor aur ghul ho aur na takleef aur eza  ki koi baat. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- (من قصبٍ) sey murad moti key baans hain."
3877,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : ''duniya ki aurton mein sab sey behtar (apney zamaney mein) Khadeeja binte Khuwelid thin aur duniya ki aurton mein sab sey behtar (apney zamaney mein) Maryam binte Imran thin.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein , Anas , ibne-Abbas aur Aaisha (Raziallauh anhum) sey ahadees aai hain."
3878,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''sari duniya ki aurton mein sey tumhen Maryam binte Imran, Khadeeja binte khuwelid, Fatima binte Muhammad, aur Firon ki biwi Aasiya kafi hain.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees sahih hai."
3879,"log apney hadiye tohfey bhejney key liye Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) key din (baari key din) ki talash mein rehtey they, to meri saukanein sab Umme-Salma (Raziallahu Anha) key yahan jama huin, aur kehney lagin : Umme-Salma ! log apney hadaya bhejney key liye Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) key din ki talash mein rehtey hain aur hum sab bhi khair ko isi tarah chaahne wale hain jaisey Aaisha hain, to tum Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ja kar kaho ke aap logon sey keh den ke aap jahan bhi hon (yani jis key yahan bhi baari ho) wo log wahin aap ko hadaya bheja karen, chunanche Umme-Salma ney iska zikr Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey kiya, to aap ney aeraz kiya, aur un ki baat ki taraf koi tawajjoh nahin di, phir aap un ki taraf paltey to unhoney apni baat phir dohraai aur bolin : meri saukanein kehti hain ke log apney hadaaya key liye Aaisha ki baari ki taag mein rehtey hain to aap logon sey keh den ke aap jahan bhi hun wo hadiye bheja karen, phir jab unhoney teesri baar aap sey yehi kaha to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Umme-Salma tum Aaisha key silsiley mein mujhey na sataao kyonkey Aaisha key ilawa tum sab mein sey koi aurat aisi nahin jis key lihaaf mein mujh par ""wahi"" utri ho.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- baaz raawiyon ney is hadees ko Hammad bin Zaid sey , Hammad ney Hisham bin Urwa sey aur Hisham ney apney baap Urwa key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey mursalan riwayat kiya hai. 3- ye hadees Hisham bin Urwa key tareeq sey Auf bin Haris sey bhi aai hai jisey Auf bin Haris ney Rameesa key wastey sey Umme-Salma (Raziallahu Anha) sey iska kuchh hissa riwayat kiya hai, Hisham bin Urwa sey marvi ye hadees mukhtalif tariqon sey aai hai. 4- Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Bilal ney bhi b-tareeq : ( هشام بن عروة an أبيه an عائشة) Hammad bin Zaid ki hadees ki tarah riwayat ki hai."
3880,"Jibreel (Alaihissalam) eik sabz (hara) resham key tukdey par un ki tasweer ley kar Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaye, aur kaha : ye aap ki biwi hain, duniya aur aakhirat dono mein. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf Abdullah bin Amr bin Alqama ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 2- Abdur-Rehman bin Mehdi ney is hadees ko Abdullah bin Amr bin Alqama sey isi sanad sey mursalan riwayat kiya hai aur is mein Aaisha sey riwayat ka zikr nahin kiya hai. 3- abu-Usaama ney is hadees key kuchh hissey ko Hisham bin Urwa sey, unhoney apney baap sey, unhoney Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kiya hai."
3881,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Aaisha ! ye Jibreel hain, tumhen salam keh rahey hain, mainey arz kiya : aur unhen bhi meri taraf sey salam aur Allah ki rahmatein aur barkaten hon, aap wo dekhtey hain jo hum nahin dekh paatey'' (jaisey Jibreel ko). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3882,mujh sey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Jibreel tumhen salam keh rahey hain to mainey arz kiya : un par salam aur Allah ki rahmatein aur uski barkaten hon.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees sahih hai.
3883,hum as-haabe Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam par jab bhi koi hadees mushkil hoti aur hamney uskey barey mein Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey puchha to hamen unkey paas uskey barey mein koi jaankari zarur mili. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai.
3884,mainey Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey ziyada faseeh (behtareen kalam) kisi ko nahin dekha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hi : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai.
3885,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney unhen lashkar zaatus-salaasil ka ameer muqarrar kiya, wo kehtey hain : to main aap ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! logon mein aap ko sab sey ziyada mehbub kon hai? aap ney farmaya : ''Aaisha''  mainey puchha : mardon mein kon hai? aap ney farmaya : ''un key baap''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3886,unhoney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! logon mein aap ko sab sey ziyada mehbub kon hai? aap ney farmaya : ''Aaisha''  unhoney puchha : mardon mein? aap ney farmaya : ''un key walid''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey yani Ismail ki riwayat sey jisey wo Qais sey riwayat kartey hain Hasan gharib hai.
3887,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aurton par Aaisha ki fazilat isi tarah hai jaisey sareed ki fazilat doosrey khaanon par hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- is bab mein Aaisha , abu-Musa Ash-ari sey ahadees aai hain. 3- Abdullah bin Abdur-Rehman bin Maamar Ansari sey murad Abu Tawaala Ansari Madni hain aur wo Suqa (bharosemand) hain, un sey Malik bin Anas ney bhi riwayat ki hai."
3888,"eik shakhs ney Ammar bin Yasir (Raziallahu anhu) key paas Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki buraai ki to unhoney kaha : hat mardud badtar, kya to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki mehbuba ko aziyat pahuncha raha hai? Imam Tirmizi kehtey hi : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3889,"mainey Ammar bin Yasir (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huye suna ke ye yani Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) duniya aur aakhirat dono mein aap ki biwi hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- is bab mein Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
3890,aap sey arz kiya gaya : Allah key Rasool ! logon mein aap ko sab sey ziyada mehbub kon hai? aap ney farmaya : ''Aaisha''  arz kiya gaya mardon mein? aap ney farmaya : ''un key walid.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey yani Anas ki riwayat sey Hasan sahih gharib hai.
3891,"Fajr key baad ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey kaha gaya ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki azwaj (jodey) (biwiyon) mein sey falan ka intiqal ho gaya, to wo sajde mein gir gaey, un sey puchha gaya : kya ye sajda karney ka waqt hai? to unhoney kaha : kya Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney ye nahin farmaya : ''jab tum Allah ki taraf sey koi khofnak baat dekho to sajda karo''  to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key azwaj (jodey) (biwi) key duniya sey rukhsat honey sey badi aur kon si ho sakti hai?''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
3892,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam merey paas tashrif laye, mujhey Hafsa aur Aaisha Raziallahu anhuma ki taraf sey eik (takleef deh) baat pahunchi thi jisey mainey aap sey zikr kiya to aap ney farmaya : tum ney ye kyon nahin kaha? ke tum dono mujh sey behtar kaisey ho sakti ho, merey shohar Muhammad Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam hain aur baap Harun hain, aur chacha Musa hain aur jo baat pahunchi thi wo ye thi ke Hafsa aur Aaisha Raziallahu anhuma ney kaha tha ke hum Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key nazdik un sey ziyada ba-izzat hain, isliye ke hum Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki azwaj (jodey) hain, aur aap key chacha ki betiyan hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- Safiya ki is hadees ko Haashim Koofi ki riwayat sey jantey hain, aur iski sanad ziyada qawi nahin hai. 3- is bab mein Anas sey bhi riwayat hai,"
3893,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Fateh Makka key saal Fatima ko bulaya aur unkey kaan mein kuchh baaten kahin to wo ro padin , phir aap ney dobara un sey kuchh kaha to wo hansney lagin, phir jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam wafat paa gaey to mainey un sey unkey roney aur hansney ki wajeh poochhi to unhoney kaha ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujhey ye bataya tha ke anqarib aap wafat paa jaeyngey, to (ye sun kar) main roney lagi thi, phir aap ney jab mujhey ye bataya ke Maryam binte Imran ko chhod kar main ehale jannat ki tamam aurton ki sardar hongi, to ye sun kar main hansney lagi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai."
3894,"Ummul-momenin Safiya (Raziallahu Anha) ko ye baat pahunchi ke Ummul-momenin Hafsa (Raziallahu Anha) ney unhen Yahudi ki beti honey ka taana diya hai, to wo roney lagin, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam unkey paas aaye to wo ro rahi thin, aap ney puchha : tum kyon ro rahi ho? to unhoney kaha : Hafsa ney mujhey ye taana diya hai ke main Yahudi ki beti hun, to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tu eik Nabi ki beti hai, tera chacha bhi Nabi hai padhi. aur to eik Nabi key nikah mein hai, to wo kis baat mein tujh par fakhr kar rahi hai, phir aap ney (Hafsa sey) farmaya : ''Hafsa ! Allah sey dar.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai."
3895,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' tum mein sey behtar wo hai jo apney ghar walon key liye behtar ho aur main apney ghar walon key liye sab sey behtar hun aur jab tum mein sey koi mar jaey to usey khair baad keh do, yani uski buraiyon ko yad na karo.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Sory ki riwayat sey Hasan gharib sahih hai aur Sory sey riwayat karney waley isey kitney kam log hain aur ye hadees Hisham bin Urwa sey Urwa key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey mursalan bhi aai hai."
3896,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''merey as-haab mein sey koi kisi ki burai mujh tak na pahunchaey, kyonkey mein ye pasand karta hun ke jab main un ki taraf niklun to mera Sina saaf ho.''  Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : (eik baar) Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas kuchh maal aaya aur aap ney isey taqseem kar diya, to main do aadmiyon key paas pahuncha jo bethey huye they aur keh rahey they : qism Allah ki ! Muhammad ney apni is taqseem sey jo unhoney ki hai na razaae-Ilaahi talab ki hai na daare-aakhirat, jab mainey usey suna to ye baat mujhey buri lagi, chunanche main Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaya aur aap ko uski khabar di to aap ka chehra surkh ho gaya aur aap ney farmaya : ''mujhey janey do kyonkey Musa ko to is sey bhi ziyada sataya gaya phir bhi unhoney sabr kiya.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai aur is sanad main eik aadmi ka izafa kar diya gaya hai."
3897,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''koi kisi ki koi baat mujhey na pahunchaey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is hadees ka kuchh hissa is sanad key ilawa sey bhi Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey marfooan aaya hai.
3898,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un sey farmaya : ''Allah ney mujhey hukm diya hai ke main tumhen Quran padh kar sunaaun, chunanche aap ney unhen « لم يكن الذين كفروا » padh kar sunaya, is mein ye baat bhi ke beshak Deen wali, Allah key nazdik tamam deenon sey kat kar Allah ki janib yaksu ho janey wali musalman aurat hai, na Yahudi , nasrani aur majusi aurat , jo koi neki kerega to uski na-qadri hergiz nahin ki jaeygi aur aap ney unhen ye bhi bataya ke insan key paas maal sey bhari hui eik wadi ho to wo dusri bhi chahega , aur agar usey dusri mil jaey to teesri chahega , aur insan ka pet sirf mitti hi bhar sakeygi aur Allah usi ki tauba qubul karta hai jo waqae tauba karey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye hadees iskey ilawa dusri sanadon sey bhi aai hai, isey Abdullah bin Abdur-Rehman bin Abzi ney apney walid sey unhoney Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kiya hai ke Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un sey farmaya : ''Allah ney mujhey hukm diya hai ke main tumhen Quran padh kar sunaaun.''  3- isey Qatada ney Anas sey riwayat kiya hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Ubai-bin Kaab sey farmaya : ''Allah ney mujhey hukm diya hai ke main tumhen Quran padh kar sunaaun.''"
3899,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''agar hijrat na hoti to main bhi ansaar hi ka eik fard hota.''  isi sanad sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ye bhi riwayat hai ke aap ney farmaya : ''agar ansaar kisi wadi ya ghaati mein chalen to main bhi unhen key sath hunga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai.
3900,"unhoney Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey suna, ya kaha ke Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney ansaar key barey mein farmaya : ''un sey momin hi mohabbat karta hai, aur un sey munafiq hi bughz rakhta hai, jo un sey mohabbat kerega us sey Allah mohabbat kerega aur jo un sey bughz rakheyga us sey Allah bughz rakheyga.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees sahih hai."
3901,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney (Fateh Makka key waqt) ansaar key kuchh logon ko ikhatta kiya padhi. aur farmaya : ''kya tumharey ilawa tum mein koi aur hai?'' logon ney arz kiya : nahin siwaye hamarey bhaanjey key, to aap ney farmaya : ''qom ka bhaanjaa to qom hi mein dakhil hota hai.''  phir aap ney farmaya : ''Quraish apni jahiliyat aur (kufr ki) musibat sey nikal kar abhi naey naey Islam laye hain. mein chahta hun ke kuchh un ki diljoi karun aur unhen manus karun, (isi liye maale ghanimat mein sey unhen diya hai) kya tum ye pasand nahin kartey ke log duniya ley kar apney gharon ko loten aur tum Allah key Rasool ko ley kar apney ghar jaao.''  logon ney arz kiya : kyon nahin, hum is par razi hain, phir Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''agar log eik wadi ya ghaati mein chalen aur ansaar dusri wadi ya ghaati mein chalen to main ansaar ki wadi aur ghaati mein chalunga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3902,"unhoney Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ko khat likha us khat mein wo un ki un logon key silsiley mein ta'ziyat (shok) kar rahey they jo unkey ghar walon mein sey aur chacha key beton mein sey Harra key din kaam aagey they to unhoney (us khat mein) unhen likha : main aap ko Allah ki taraf sey eik khushkhabri sunata hun, mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey suna hai aap ney farmaya : ''aey Allah ! ansaar ko, un ki aulad ko, aur un ki aulad ki aulad ko bakhsh dey.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- isey Qatada ney bhi Nazar bin Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey aur unhoney Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kiya hai."
3903,"mujh sey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum apni qom padhi. ko salam kaho, kyonkey wo paakbaz aur sabir log hain jaisa ke mujhey malum hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3904,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''meri jaama-daani jiski taraf main panah leta hun yani merey khas log merey ehale-bait hain, aur merey raz daar aur ameen ansaar hain to tum in key khata kaaron ko darguzar karo aur in key bhaley logon ki achchhaiyon ko qubul karo.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Anas sey bhi riwayat hai,"
3905,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo Quraish ki ruswai chahega Allah usey ruswa kar dega.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai. 2- hum sey Abd bin Humaid ney bayan kiya, wo kehtey hain : mujhey Yaqub bin Ibrahim bin Saad ney khabar di, wo kehtey hain : mujh sey merey walid ney bayan kiya aur unhoney Saleh bin Kaisaan sey aur Saleh ney ibne Shahab sey isi sanad sey isi jaisi hadees riwayat ki."
3906,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''koi shakhs jo Allah aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhta ho ansaar sey bughz nahin rakh sakta.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
3907,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''ansaar merey raz daar aur merey khaasam-khaas hain, log anqarib badhengey aur ansaar kam hotey jaeyngey, to tum unkey bhaley logon ki achchhaaiyon ko qubul karo aur unkey khata-kaaron ki khataaon sey darguzar karo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3908,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aey Allah ! Quraish key pehlon ko tu ney (qatl, qaid aur zillat ka ( azab chakhaya hai, to in key pichhlon ko bakhshish aur inayat sey nawaz dey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
3909,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : « اللهم اغفر للأنصار ولأبناء الأنصار ولأبناء أبناء الأنصار ولنساء الأنصار » ''aey Allah ! ansaar ko , unkey beton ko , unkey beton key beton ko aur un ki aurton ko bakhsh dey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai."
3910,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''kya main tumhen ansaar key behtar gharon ki ya ansaar key behtar logon ki khabar na dun? logon ney arz kiya : kyon nahin Allah key Rasool ! aap ney farmaya : ''sab sey behtar bani Najaar hain, phir bani Abdul-Ash'hal hain jo un sey qarib hain, phir bani Haris bin Khazraj hain jo un sey qarib hain, phir bani Saaida hain padhi. , phir aap ney apney dono haathon sey ishara kiya aur apni ungliyon ko band kiya, phir khola jaisey koi apney haathon sey kuchh phenk raha ho.'' aur farmaya : ''ansaar key sarey gharon mein khair hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Anas sey bhi aai hai jisey wo abu-Usaid Saaidi key wastey sey Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kartey hain."
3911,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''ansaar key gharon mein sab sey behtar ghar bani Najaar key ghar padhi. hain, phir bani Abdul-Ash'hal key, phir bani Haris bin Khazraj key phir bani Saaida key aur ansaar key sarey gharon mein khair hai.''  to Saad ney kaha : main Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko yehi samajh raha hun ke aap ney hum par logon ko fazilat di hai padhi. to un sey kaha gaya : aap ko bhi to bahut sey logon par fazilat di hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Abu-Usaid Saaidi ka naam Malik bin Rabeea hai. 3- isi jaisi riwayat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi marfoo tareeqe sey aai hai. 4- isey Maamar ney Zohri sey , Zohri ney abu-Salma aur Ubedullah bin Abdullah bin Utba sey aur in dono ney Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) key wastey sey Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai."
3912,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''ansaar key gharon mein sab sey behtar ghar bani Najaar key ghar hain.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai.
3913,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''ansaar mein sab sey behtar bani Abdul-Ash'hal hain.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai.
3914,"hum Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath nikley yahan tak ke jab hum Harra suqya mein pahunchey jo Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) ka mohalla tha to Rasulullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : (اللهم إن إبراهيم كان عبدك وخليلك ودعا لأهل مكة بالبركة وأنا عبدك ورسولك أدعوك لأهل المدينة أن تبارك لهم في مدهم وصاعهم مثلي ما باركت لأهل مكة مع البركة بركتين) ''mujhey wuzu ka pani do''  chunanche aap ney wuzu kiya, phir aap qibla rukh khadey huye aur farmaya : ''aey Allah ! Ibrahim terey bandey aur terey dost hain aur unhoney ehale Makka key liye barkat ki dua farmaaey, aur main tera banda aur tera Rasool hun, aur tujh sey ehale Madina key liye dua karta hun ke to in key mudd aur in ki saa mein ehale Makka ko jo tu ney barkat di hai uski do gunaa barkat farma, aur har barkat key sath do barkaten (yani ehale Makka ki doguni barkat ata farma).'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Aaisha , Abdullah bin Zaid aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey ahadees aai hain."
3915,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''merey ghar aur merey member key darmiyan (Masjide Nabuwi) jo hissa hai wo jannat ki kyariyon mein sey eik kiyaari hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai, aur ye hadees Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey is sanad key ilawa dusri sanadon sey bhi marfooan aai hai."
3916,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''merey ghar aur merey member key darmiyan jo hissa hai wo jannat ki kyariyon mein sey eik kiyaari hai.''
3917,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo Madine mein mar sakta ho to usey chahiye ke wahin marey kyonkey jo wahan mareyga main uskey haq mein sifarish karunga.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey yani Ayub sakhtiyaan ki riwayat sey Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Sabeeaa binte Haris Aslamiya sey bhi riwayat hai,"
3918,"un ki eik azad karda laundi unkey paas aai aur un sey kehney lagi main gardishe zamana ki shikar hun aur Iraaq jana chahti hun, to unhoney kaha : to Sham kyon nahin chali jati jo hashr aur nashr ki sar zamin hai, (aap ney kaha) « اصبري لكاع » ! kyonkey mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna hai : ''jisney uski (Madina ki) sakhti aur tangi maeeshat par sabr kiya to main qiyamat key din uskey liye gawah ya sifarishi hunga.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Ubedullah ki riwayat sey Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- is bab mein abu Saeed Khudri, Sufiyan bin Abi Zuhair aur Sabeeaa Aslamiya (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
3919,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Islam key shehron mein viraani key aetbar sey Madina sab sey aakhiri shehar hoga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf Junaada ki riwayat sey jantey hain, jisey wo Hisham bin Urwa sey riwayat kartey hain. 2- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ney is hadees key Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) par tajjub ka izhar kiya hai (yani aisi baat kaisey sahih ho sakti hai)."
3920,"eik Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey Islam par baiat ki, phir usey Madina mein bukhar aa gaya to wo Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam paas aaya aur kehney laga , aap mujhey meri baiat pher den, to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney inkar kiya, phir wo dobara aap key paas aaya aur kehney laga : aap meri baiat mujhey pher den to phir aap ney inkar kiya, phir wo Erabi (dehati) Madina chhod kar chala gaya to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Madina eik bhatti key misl (jaisa) hai jo door kar deta hai apney khot ko aur khalis kar deta hai paak ko.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
3921,"agar main Madine mein hirnon ko chartey dekhon to unhen na daraao isliye ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya hai : ''iski dono pathreeli zaminon padhi. key darmiyan ka hissa Haram hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Saad , Abdullah bin Zaid , Anas , abu-Ayyub , Zaid bin Sabit , Raafey bin Khadees, Sehal bin Hanif aur Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
3922,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko uhad pahad nazar aaya to aap ney farmaya : ''ye aisa pahad hai ke ye hum sey mohabbat karta hai aur hum is sey, aey Allah ! Ibrahim ney Makka ko haram kiya aur main is (Madine) ki dono pathreeli zaminon key beech key hissey ko haram qarar dey raha hun.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3923,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah ney meri taraf ""wahi"" ki ke Madina, Behrein aur Qinnsareen in teeno mein sey jahan bhi tum jaao wohi tumhara daarul-hijrat hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf Fazal bin Musa ki riwayat sey jantey hain aur un sey Abu Ammar yani Husain bin Hures riwayat karney mein munfarid (alag) hain."
3924,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Madina ki tangi maeeshat (arthviyavastha) aur uski sakhtiyon par jo sabr kerega main qiyamat key din uskey liye gawah aur sifarishi hunga.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai. 2- is bab mein abu Saeed Khudri, Sufiyan bin Abi Zuhair aur Sabeeaa Aslamiya (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain. 3- Saleh bin Abi Saleh Suhel bin Abi Saleh key bhai hain."
3925,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko « حزوراء » (chhote teele) par khadey dekha, aap ney farmaya : ''qasam Allah ki ! bilashuba to Allah ki sar zamin mein sab sey behtar hai aur Allah ki zaminon mein Allah key nazdik sab sey mehbub sar zamin hai, agar mujhey tujh sey na nikala jata to main na nikalta.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai. 2- isey Yunus ney bhi Zohri sey isi tarah riwayat kiya hai, aur isey Muhammad bin Amr ney ba-tareeq : (abi Salma an abi Huraira an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam) riwayat kiya hai, aur Zohri ki hadees jo ba-tareeq : (أبي سلمة an عبد الله بن عدي ابن حمراء) aai hai wo merey nazdik ziyada sahih hai."
3926,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Makka ko khitab kartey huye farmaya : ''kitna pakizah shehar hai to aur to kitna mujhey mehbub hai, meri qom ney mujhey tujh sey na nikala hota to main terey ilawa kahin aur na rehta.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai."
3927,"mujh sey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Salman ! tum mujh sey bughz na rakho ke tumhara Deen haath sey jata rahey.''  mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! main kaisey aap sey bughz rakh sakta hun aur haal ye hai ke Allah ney aap hi key zariye hamein hidayat bakhshi hai, aap ney farmaya : ''tum Arbon sey bughz rakhogey to mujh sey bughz rakhogey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf Abu Badr Shujaa bin Waleed ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 2- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey suna : Abu-Zibyaan ney Salman ka zamana nahin paya hai aur Salman Ali sey pehley wafat paa gaey they."
3928,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney Arbon ko dhoka diya wo meri shafaat mein shamil na hoga aur usey meri mohabbat nasib na hogi.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- hum isey sirf Husain bin umr Ahmasi ki riwayat sey jantey hain aur wo Makhaariq sey riwayat kartey hain, aur Husain muhaddeseen key nazdik ziyada qawi nahin hain."
3929,"jab koi Arab martaa to Umme Jareer par uski maut badi sakht ho jati yani unhen zabardast sadma hota to un sey kaha gaya ke hum aap ko dekhtey hain ke jab koi Arab martaa hai to aap ko bahut sadma pahunchta hai? to unhoney kaha : mainey apney Malik ko kehtey huye suna hai ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''arbon ki halakat qurbe qiyamat ki nishani hai.'' Muhammad bin Rizeen kehtey hain : unkey Malik ka naam Talha bin Malik hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Harab ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
3930,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''log Dajjaal sey bhagengey, yahan tak ke pahadon par ja rahengey.''  Umme Shareek (Raziallahu Anha) ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! us waqt Arab kahan hongey? aap ney farmaya : ''wo (tadaad mein) thodey hongey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
3931,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''(Saam) Arbon key puraane buzurg hain aur (یافث) Romiyon key aur (حام) habshiyon key.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai aur « یافث » , padhi. « یافِتُ » aur « یَفِتُ » teeno lughte hain."
3932,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas ajam (ghair-arab) ka zikr kiya gaya to aap ney farmaya : ''mujhey un par ya unkey baaz logon par tum sey ya tumharey baaz logon sey ziyada aitimad hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai hum isey sirf abu-Bakar bin Ayash ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 2- aur Saleh bin Abi Saleh ko Saleh bin Mehran Mola Amr bin Hures bhi kaha jata hai.
3933,"jis waqt Sura-Jumuaa nazil hui hum Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas mojud they, aap ney iski tilawat farmaaee, jab « وآخرين منهم لما يلحقوا بهم » par pahunchey to aap sey eik shakhs ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! ye kon log hain jo abhi hum sey miley nahin hain to aap ney isey koi jawab nahin diya, wo kehtey hain : aur Salman Faarsi hum mein mojud they, to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney apna haath Salman key ooper rakha aur farmaya : ''qasam hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai agar eman surayyaa par bhi hoga to bhi uskey kuchh log usey hasil kar lein gey.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- aur ye mutaaddid (bahut si) sanadon sey Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marfoo tareeqe sey aai hai."
3934,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Yamen ki taraf dekha aur farmaya : ''aey Allah ! unkey dilon ko hamari taraf pher dey aur hamarey saa aur mudd mein hamein barkat dey.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, hum isey yani Zaid bin Sabit ki is hadees ko sirf Imran Qataan ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
3935,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tumharey paas ehale Yamen aaye wo naram dil aur naram mizaj hain, eman Yamni hai aur hikmat bhi Yamni hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas aur ibne-Masood (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
3936,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Saltanat (hukoomat) Quraish mein rahegi, aur qaza Ansaar mein aur Azan Habsha mein aur amanat qabila Azd mein yani Yamen mein.''"
3937,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''(Azd) (ehale-Yamen) zamin mein Allah key sher hain, log unhen giraana chahtey hain aur Allah unhen uthana chahta hai, aur logon par eik aisa zamana bhi aayega ke aadmi kaheyga, kaash! ! mera baap Azdi hota, kaash! meri maa ! Azdi hoti.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 2- ye hadees is sanad sey Anas sey maqoof tareeqe sey aai hai, aur ye hamarey nazdik ziyada sahih hai."
3938,agar hum Azdi (yani qabila Azd key) na hon to hum aadmi hain hi nahin. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai.
3939,"hum Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas they ke itney main eik shakhs aaya (mera khayal hai ke wo qabila Qais ka tha) aur usney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! qabila Hameer par lanat farmaiye, to aap ney us sey chehra pher liya, phir wo dusri taraf sey aap key paas aaya, aap ney phir us sey apna chehra pher liya, phir wo dusri taraf sey aaya to aap ney phir apna chehra pher liya, phir wo dusri taraf sey aaya to aap ney apna chehra pher liya aur farmaya : ''Allah Hameer par reham karey, unkey munh mein salam hai, unkey haath mein khana hai, aur wo aman aur eman waley log hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey Abdur-Razzaaq ki riwayat sey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 2- aur Meenaa sey bahut si munkir hadisein riwayat ki jati hain."
3940,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Ansaar, Muzena, Juhaina, Ghifaar, Ashja' aur jo qabila Abduddaar key hon wo merey rafeeq hain, unka Allah key ilawa koi aur rafeeq nahin, aur Allah aur uskey Rasool unkey rafeeq hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3941,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''bani Aslam ko Allah sahih Salim rakhey, Ghifaar ko Allah bakhshey aur Usba (qabeela) ney Allah aur uskey Rasool ki nafarmani ki.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3942,"logon ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! Saqeef key teeron ney hamen zakhmi kar diya, to aap Allah sey unkey liye bad dua farmaeyn, aap ney farmaya : (اللهم اهد ثقيفا) ''aey Allah ! Saqeef ko hidayat dey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
3943,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki wafat hui aur aap teen qabeelon Saqeef, bani-Haneefa aur bani Umayya ko napasand kartey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
3944,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Saqeef main eik jhoota aur eik tabahi machaney wala zalim shakhs hoga.''
3945,"eik Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko eik jawan oontni hadiye mein di, aur aap ney iskey iwaz mein usey chhe oontniyaan inayat farmaeen, phir bhi wo aap sey khafa raha ye khabar Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko pahunchi to aap ney Allah ki hamd aur sanaa ki phir farmaya : ''falan ney mujhey eik oontni hadiye mein di thi, mainey uskey iwaz mein usey chhe jawan oontniyaan den, phir bhi wo naraz raha, mainey irada kar liya hai ke ab siwaye Quraishi, ya Ansari, ya Saqafi ya Dosi key kisi ka hadiya qubul na karun.'' is hadees mein mazeed kuchh aur baaten bhi hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees mutaaddid (bahut si) sanadon sey Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey aai hai. 2- aur Yazeed bin Harun Ayub Abul Aala sey riwayat kartey hain, aur wo Ayub bin Miskeen hain aur inhen ibne-Abi Miskeen bhi kaha jata hai, aur shayad yehi wo hadees hai jisey unhoney Ayub sey aur Ayub ney Saeed Maqbari sey riwayat ki hai, aur Ayub sey murad Ayub  Abul Aala hain."
3946,"qabila bani Fazara key eik shakhs ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko apney un oonton mein sey jo usey ghaaba mein miley they eik oontni hadiya mein di to aap ney usey uska kuchh iwaz diya, lekin wo aap sey khafa raha, to mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko member par farmatey suna ke ''arbon mein sey kuchh log mujhey hadiya detey hain aur uskey badle mein unhen jis qadr merey paas hota hai main deta hun, phir bhi wo khafa rehte hai aur barabar mujh sey apni narazgi jatate rehte hai, qism Allah ki ! iskey baad main Arbon mein sey kisi bhi aadmi ka hadiya qubul nahin karunga siwaye Quraishi, Ansari ya Saqafi ya Dosii key.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai aur ye Yazeed bin Harun ki riwayat sey jisey wo Ayub sey riwayat kartey hain ziyada sahih hai."
3947,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''kya hi achchhey hain qabila Asad aur qabila Ash'ar key log, jo ladaai sey bhagtey nahin aur na maale-ghanimat mein khayanat kartey hain, wo mujh sey hain aur main un sey hun.''  Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : phir mainey usey Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) sey bayan kiya to unhoney kaha : is tarah Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney nahin farmaya, balke aap ney ye farmaya ke ''wo mujh sey hain aur meri taraf hain.''  to mainey arz kiya : merey baap ney mujh sey is tarah nahin bayan kiya, balke unhoney mujh sey bayan kiya ke mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna hai : ''wo mujh sey hain aur main un sey hun.''  Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : to tum apney baap ki hadeeson key ziyada jaankar ho. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf Wahab bin Jareer ki riwayat sey jantey hain aur kaha jata hai ke Asad qabila Asad hi key log hain."
3948,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah qabila Aslam ko salaamat rakhey aur bani Ghifaar ko Allah ko bakhshey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Abu-Zar , abu-Barza Aslami aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey hi ahadees aai hain."
3949,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah qabila Aslam ko salaamat rakhey aur Ghifaar ko Allah bakhsh dey aur Usba ney Allah aur uskey Rasool ki nafarmani ki.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
3950,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''qasam hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein Muhammad ki jaan hai ! Ghifaar, Aslam, Muzaina aur jo Juhaina key log'' ya aap ney farmaya : ''Juhaina aur jo Muzaina key log hain Allah key nazdik qiyamat key din Asad, Tai aur Ghatfaan sey behtar hongey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3951,"qabila bani Tameem key log Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki khidmat mein aaye to aap ney farmaya : ''aey bani Tameem ! khush ho jaao.'' wo log kehney lagey : aap ney hamein basharat di hai, to (kuchh) dijiye, wo kehtey hain : ye sun kar Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka chehra Mubarak mutghaiyar ho (badal) gaya, itney mein Yamen key kuchh log aagey to aap ney farmaya : ''tumhin log basharat qubul kar lo.''  jab bani Tameem ney isey qubul nahin kiya to un logon ney kaha : hamney qubul kar liya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3952,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''qabaayel Aslam, Ghifaar aur Muzena, qabaayel Tameem , Asad , Ghatfaan aur bani Aamir bin Sa'saa sey behtar hain.''  aur aap iskey sath apni aawaz oonchi kar rahey they, to log kehney lagey : na-murad huye aur khasarey mein rahey, aap ney farmaya : ''wo un (qabaayel yani Tameem, Asad, Ghatfaan aur bani Aamir bin Sa'saa) sey behtar hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3953,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aey Allah ! hamarey Sham mein barkat ata farma, aey Allah ! hamarey Yamen mein barkat ata farma.''  logon ney arz kiya : aur hamarey Najad mein, aap ney farmaya : ''aey Allah ! hamarey Sham mein barkat ata farma, aur hamarey Yamen mein barkat ata farma'' ,logon ney arz kiya : aur hamarey Najad mein, aap ney farmaya : '' yahan zalzaley aur fitney hain, aur usi sey shetan ki seeng niklegi.''  (yani shetan ka lashkar aur uskey madadgar niklengey). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey yani ibne Aun ki riwayat sey Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- ye hadees ba-tareeq : (Saalim bin Abdullah bin umr an Abeeh an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam) bhi aai hai."
3954,"hum log Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas kaghaz key purzon sey Quran ko murattab kar rahey they, to aap ney farmaya : ''mubarak baadi ho Sham key liye.''  hamney arz kiya : kis chiz ki aey Allah key Rasool ! aap ney farmaya : ''is baat ki ke Rehman key farishtey unkey liye apney bazu bichhate hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf Yahya bin Ayub ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
3955,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''baaz aa jaeyn wo qomen jo apney un aabaa-o-ijdaad par fakhr kar rahi hain jo mar gaey hain, wo jahannam ka koila hain warna wo Allah key nazdik us gubreele sey bhi ziyada zaleel ho jaeyngey, jo apney aagey apni naak sey najasat dhakelta rehta hai, Allah ney tum sey jahiliyat ki nakhwat (ghamand) ko khatam kar diya hai, ab to log momin aur muttaqi hain ya faajir aur bad-bakht, log sab key sab Adam ki aulad hain aur Adam mitti sey paida kiye gaey hain.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey hadeesen aai hain."
3956,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah ney tum sey jahiliyat ki nakhwat (ghamand) aur apney baap dada par fakhr ko khatam kar diya hai, ab log momin aur muttaqi hain ya faajir aur bad-bakht aur sarey log Adam ki aulad hain aur Adam mitti sey banaey gaey hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan aur ye hamarey nazdik pehli riwayat sey ziyada sahih hai. 2- Saeed Maqbari ney Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey suna hai aur wo apney baap key wastey sey bahut si cheezen Abu-Hurera sey riwayat kartey hain. 3- Sufiyan Sory aur kaee doosrey raawiyon ney ye hadees Hisham bin Saad sey, Hisham ney Saeed Maqbari sey aur Saeed Maqbari ney Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) key wastey sey Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey Abu-Aamir ki hadees key maanind riwayat ki hai jisey wo Hisham bin Saad sey riwayat kartey hain."
